\id REV - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG REVELATION 1 13/2/91 Macnaughtan 
\h PENEME YAEYEKEEKI 
\toc1 Dotaęž‰ Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaeyekeeki 
\toc2 Peneme Yaeyekeeki 
\toc3 Peneme Yaeyekeeki 
\mt1 Dotaęž‰ Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaeyekeeki  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Do bukataęž‰ mo Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ peneme yaeyeke haumanu lao ulaęž‰ bukae. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do peneme yaasaęž‰ haumanu haleeke ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ koto kone pulu piekeeki waluekemaęž‰ piekeme. Ketisomaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo tapao dupiki haumanu walenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeeke haumanu paeyao laęž‰laęž‰me. Do lao ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pi make Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ otaęž‰ tupaęž‰ peneme yaalaęž‰ pie.   
\p
\v 3 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do buka paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekimanu ipulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰me. Kutupa make epi amedamaęž‰ do laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pimanu opitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki tukiki nane mendimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke do haumanu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰leke loaęž‰me.   
\s1 Watake hataęž‰ siosi paęž‰taęž‰ wape tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 4 IĚ±taęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ mo Eisia kenke nane halaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ alome. Ame do make halaęž‰ ambaęž‰ make hayeke wetepenaęž‰ make epolo paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kinaęž‰e. Koto tupaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke pilaęž‰ sea tikitikinaęž‰ haleme watake hataęž‰ sipitidi manumaęž‰ make kinaęž‰e.  
\v 5 Kutupa make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi otaęž‰ tupaęž‰ laasaęž‰ hali mo hande homaęž‰laęž‰eki bepolao tiaeyeke titinaęž‰ hali make do kenke honiki paeyaonaęž‰ kini haliwekinaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ make homeke hau kone pinaęž‰e.  
\p Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki pukimaęž‰ homo halaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ lopeeke wemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ niki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokomono nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yeni peao haleme wandaęž‰hali hamono laęž‰laęž‰me. Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make hoto paeyao pa utia pu haenaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 7 Ipikitaęž‰ ya hapi manda oli ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Paeyaomaęž‰ handilimikie. Mo ipiki ikoko lia dolomaęž‰ awemeke haliwekinaęž‰ make loaęž‰me. Kutupa do kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki handolo hataęž‰ eĚ± tieke lelimikie. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kutu pilieke.   
\p
\v 8 Mo Aneke Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ otaęž‰ wetepe sale nane makee laa IĚ±taęž‰ ame do halo make ambaęž‰ haowaęž‰ make wetepenaęž‰ make epolo polo halie alaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\s1 Dionimaęž‰ Ketiso handeekeeki  
\p
\v 9 IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kame Dioni Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teliolo halie. Ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekinaęž‰ ki hone na wiki Pinaęž‰e laa tanda mineleme ekinaęž‰ putupolomaęž‰ yankekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaawaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make Yesumaęž‰ otaęž‰eki peneme yaeyekeeki walaawaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo dawalamaęž‰ dupake Paęž‰timosi kenke siki paęž‰taęž‰ hano lelememe.  
\v 10 Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ hande Sipitidimaęž‰ IĚ± handeteke hataęž‰ e pokeaęž‰me. Kutupa bu kanakenaęž‰ eĚ±maęž‰ handeke pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tiekemaęž‰ yaka hoki nane pi leaęž‰eki opuaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Dupa leaęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do handolo peleeki manutaęž‰ wape laaniao kutupa mo bukataęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ daoni manunaęž‰ siosi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaapeke. Epesese Semena Pekamamo Daetaeda Sadisi Pilaęž‰delepia make Leiodisiamanu paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi alaęž‰taęž‰ epimaęž‰ alaęž‰pe laa laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneawaęž‰pate handetaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu handoaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kutupa koto alemanu ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰taęž‰ halimaęž‰ handeke nono piki alemaęž‰ hake piki dau hokulu oni ipikaęž‰ anke anaęž‰naęž‰ wataapekeeki yameekeme. Kutupa make kolomaęž‰ wepiki beleke ipikaęž‰ hakokonaęž‰ adoto piaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Ipikaęž‰ you pitaęž‰ itiki yaapotaęž‰ mo hake pupapeke sipisipi itikimaęž‰ handa o hake pupapeke yahapimaęž‰ handeke alemaęž‰ handa make ipikaęž‰ leketaęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ ti haaleke ekimaęž‰ handeaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Ipikaęž‰ anketaęž‰ mo epeke tupaęž‰ wamo pea mulamula kitao wiki kolomaęž‰ handeke nono piki ale batasimaęž‰ handa leke yale yale peataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maketaęž‰ mo u tieke laa lopaęž‰laęž‰ ikali doĚ±uĚ±maęž‰ handeaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Ipikaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰taęž‰ watake hataęž‰ hombulankaęž‰manu miniki hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo ne hake kake yaapo hake bainasi opolu baeyaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ mo you tikekenaęž‰ talaęž‰ natemaęž‰ handeke paĚ±aĚ± tieke piaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 17 IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki handoaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ homeke halimaęž‰ handaa ipikaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ lopoaęž‰me. Kutu pueketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ popeke nane kiki IĚ± manda witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pee. IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ make otaęž‰ wetepe sale nane makee.  
\v 18 IĚ±taęž‰ deto halaęž‰ halie. IĚ±taęž‰ homoaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ tiao hoto paeyao pa hatia pu halaęž‰ hali halome. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make mo homo halaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ potaęž‰ ki handeteke halo halie.  
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ do handele alemanu paeyao make wetepe nane pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make paeyao laaniae.  
\v 20 Do yaka popeke nane miniki halo watake hataęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ manunaęž‰ make do watake hataęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu yaaponaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ teketaęž‰ dupae. Do watake hataęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ manutaęž‰ mo hande watake hataęž‰ siosi manunaęž‰ enisolomanue. Kutupa do watake hataęž‰ olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ mo hande watake hataęž‰ siosimanue leaęž‰me.   
\c 2  
\s1 Epesese siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo Epesese siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo hande watake hataęž‰ hombulankaęž‰manu ipikaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ miniki hataęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ ale ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ pominaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ tapaasaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 2 Ikaęž‰ peleme hau manutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Ikaęž‰ honkopu hao e pokelemeeki make ikaęž‰ homu pea yu wia halemeeki make loaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke haliweki na handomaęž‰ tiake make mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ aposolo haliwekie aleme tapaketaęž‰ hande hande pea diaęž‰yaotaęž‰ yayapiki pi alo lemekaęž‰taęž‰me laa handaęž‰ wilimime.  
\v 3 Ikitaęž‰ homu pea yu wia halememe. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ yaka ekinaęž‰ kone tanda nalo hataęž‰ na kiaalememe.  
\v 4 Koto pelemepate ametaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ dupa. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ IĚ± puki kitolo pimi tupaęž‰ ametaęž‰ puki na kelememe.  
\v 5 Iki pua lopeleme tupaęž‰ hone wipee. Ikaęž‰ hoke hau hoki walaa ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pimieki paa pipee. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau hoki na walemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mo ikaęž‰ olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ ale ipikaęž‰ u halaęž‰ ale minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰ lolueke.  
\v 6 Pate IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰ putiaaseme hautaęž‰ doe. IĚ±maęž‰ mo Nikoleitani tapakemaęž‰ pu haleme haumanu kiaaso pitolo tupaęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make kiaasememe.   
\p
\v 7 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ mo siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ tinaęž‰ kiliki nenaęž‰ waleke halueke.   
\s1 Semena siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 8 Mo Semena siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo hande titinaęž‰ make wetepenaęž‰ make halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ alaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ homaakaęž‰naęž‰ paa daęž‰taa halo somee alaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Ikitaęž‰ nate hali halemepate ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hamoko halememe hone ulume. Diu wandaęž‰hali diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate kone ikitaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halie lo haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pimanu lo haleme ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Sadaninaęž‰ tapakee.  
\v 10 Mo mulu peleme tanda manunaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Opiaęž‰pe. Mo Sadanimaęž‰taęž‰ iki la handolo hataęž‰ iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo dipula mea lopaalieke. Kutupa ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki manutaęž‰ kiki yaapo natenaęž‰ pua paelieke. Homaęž‰laęž‰eki epenaęž‰ kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaa pelia hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaaseme ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo peleme yenkitaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kulueke.   
\p
\v 11 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ hande hoto yaapo peao homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoeyaapeke na yelieke.   
\s1 Pekamamo siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 12 Mo Pekamamo siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo hande yaapo hao ne wopu hake bainasi wia halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ alaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Ikaęž‰ haleme paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Mo Sadanimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pu halememe. Kutupa mo Sadani halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ yaka hande hone tulao hao hataęž‰ e pokawao hayaęž‰ hali Aęž‰ntipaęž‰si lu homaeyaęž‰ nate ninaęž‰ kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao halemeeki hoki na walememe.  
\v 14 Koto pelemepate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alo pimanu dupa. Iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo Beilame walaęž‰laęž‰ pi tolu haleme wandaęž‰hali taa haleme handaęž‰e. Koto Beilame Beileke walolotaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali mo toopi ti wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ halo haleme nemanu nenaęž‰ alo make loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau pinaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ sutiaeyeke haumaęž‰ iki hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku penaęž‰yeke waleekeme.  
\v 15 Homeke tupaęž‰ kone mo hande Nikoleitani tapakenaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu tolu haleme wandaęž‰hali iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ taa haleme handaęž‰e.  
\v 16 Koto paęž‰laęž‰me ametaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau hoki walaęž‰pe. Kotoeki na pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ koto kone aęž‰pa koto wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± yaka kake paęž‰taęž‰ ipu halaęž‰ bainasimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pulueke.   
\p
\v 17 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mo aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ mandane maęž‰na halueke. Kutupa mo hake piki toopinaęž‰ panake biki laalaęž‰eki make halueke. Mo bikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make hone na ulaęž‰pate mo miliaęž‰ somemaęž‰ homeke hone wilieke.   
\s1 Daetaeda siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 18 Mo Daetaeda siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke ipikaęž‰ leketaęž‰ mo hande we pupapeke ti haaleke ekimaęž‰ handaa ipikaęž‰ anketaęž‰ mo mulamula lialeke pa leke yale yale piki kolomaęž‰ handeke ale batasimaęž‰ handeke somemaęž‰ alaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 Ikaęž‰ pu haleme hau manutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki make kimaęž‰ na homeke hone tulao halemeeki make ikaęž‰ e pokelemeeki make ikaęž‰ homu pea yu wia halemeeki make IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ametaęž‰ wopu pitelememe. Ambaęž‰ hande pimi tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me laa IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume.  
\v 20 Koto pelemepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ dupa. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ Diesibeletaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pa haenaęž‰ kiaalememe. Koto wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi mea ipulu wandaęž‰e lo halaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka e pa hameke pokaaseme tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau pinaęž‰ make mo hoke temoko paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ nemanu nenaęž‰ hatuku pu hoeyao halaęž‰me.  
\v 21 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau hoki walenaęž‰ waleke haloaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ hoki walaęž‰peke yaęž‰leke kiaasaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau pimi tapake ameĚ±leĚ± otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ tanda mulu peleme da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lopaa monealueke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu pimikieki na kelepemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do aloeki pulueke.  
\v 23 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ hoki nane tolu haleme tapake make lu homaalueke. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo siosi paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ honemanu make hone u halemeeki manunaęž‰ hone ulu somee hone wilimikie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyao ikaęž‰ peleme ekinaęž‰ homeke homeke lo anaęž‰naęž‰ kone yenki kulueke.   
\p
\v 24 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Daetaeda haleme mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hokeeki walaęž‰laęž‰eki na teliaęž‰ mea pelememe. Koto wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± haleme tapakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sadaninaęž‰ otaęž‰ oninaęž‰ tolumaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ pi tekemanue lo haleme ekitaęž‰ na mokaęž‰la handelememe. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na atulao ulueke alome.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia halemeeki manutaęž‰ IĚ± epono honkopu hao miniki hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 26 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi amedamaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaaso hataęž‰ yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pa putia pua mo honikinaęž‰ paeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handeteke hanoyeke kaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kulueke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haleme tapake paeyao handeteke hamenaęž‰ lolueke.  
\v 27 Mo ayenimaęž‰ wepieke dopitamaęž‰ handeteke hamenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo kenkemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ kanakemaęž‰ handaa yambolo sasape puemenaęž‰ lolueke.  
\v 28 Kutupa mo da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso opaęž‰laęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ halueke.   
\p
\v 29 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 3  
\s1 Sadisi siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo Sadisi siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ watake hataęž‰ sipitidimanu make mo watake hataęž‰ hombulankaęž‰manu wia halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ alaęž‰me.  
\p Ikaęž‰ piteleme hau manutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ tanda piki Ketiso wandaęž‰hali halememe lo halemeke opulupate handetaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ homaa pimikaęž‰taęž‰me.  
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ tiao mo wia haleme ale otaęž‰ homaamaęž‰naęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± tindipapee. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ peleme hau manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± tikitiki na paęž‰laęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Hande iki waleaęž‰eki opimi ekimanu niminaaso hataęž‰ opua ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± hoki walaapee. Iki aĚ±iĚ± na tiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pake nalaęž‰ hali leke opolo ipulueke. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± epolo polo natetaęž‰ hone na wilimikie.  
\v 4 Pate koto Sadisi haleme wandaęž‰hali tepo tepo aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu haĚ±iĚ± peaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hao pimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Koto peleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ hakepiki dau yama IĚ± yaapo potaęž‰ pomu halumeke. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do epeke hau peleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ dupiki hake piki dau yamilieke. Kutupa ikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ mo deto haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ na honulueke. Yaka Apaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ enisolo manunaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ peneme yao hataęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ yaka tapakee lolueke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ mo siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Pilaęž‰delepia siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 7 Mo Pilaęž‰delepia siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo yako pea otaęž‰ haunaęž‰ teke halimaęž‰ alaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Deipidinaęž‰ potaęž‰ ki wia halaęž‰ halie. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me make pokeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lombaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haleme hau manutaęž‰ hone ulume. Ikitaęž‰ honkopu hosikale siki halememe laa IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka waloloeki manutaęž‰ opua kimaęž‰ na homeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalememe. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na pokaęž‰peke yolo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki nanemaęž‰ potaęž‰ lomba wialome.  
\v 9 Opie. Mo Sadaninaęž‰ tapake yayapiki pi alo hataęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate kone ikitaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halie lo haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰puniaenaęž‰ lolueke. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki pukimaęž‰ homolome laa hone wilimikie.  
\v 10 Mo kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao la handuluekemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki handeteke halueke. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ kone kimaęž‰ na homeke honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke laa laęž‰ uaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lake pa peaęž‰tiki peleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 11 IĚ±taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia haleme ekitaęž‰ amumaęž‰ wia hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hande aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaaso hataęž‰ mimi ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ pake naamaęž‰naęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo bepolao halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ yaka Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tembolo da pinki haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ koto aletaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalieke. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yaka Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki lao make mo yaka Kodaęž‰maęž‰ oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰nialiaęž‰ hande panake daoni tieke Diutuselemenaęž‰ biki make laalueke. Kutupa make yaka panake biki laalueke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ mo siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Leiodisia siosi paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 14 Mo Leiodisia siosinaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lae. Do pitaęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ taapo wiaaso hataęž‰ Kutu pinaęž‰taa leleme somemaęž‰ alaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke otaęž‰ haunaęž‰ walo halaęž‰ halie. Kutupa make ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paeyaonaęž‰ teke somee.   
\p
\v 15 IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ peleme hau manutaęž‰ hone ulume. Iki titipu make kosaęž‰ make na paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone ulume. Ikitaęž‰ titipu make kosaęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo pinaęž‰e hone witolopate  
\v 16 ikitaęž‰ kosaęž‰ diaęž‰ titipu diaęž‰ pa tukikinaęž‰ haleme ekinaęž‰ yaka kake paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ dopita baalueke.  
\v 17 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hamoko hataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ IĚ± anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me alememe. Pate ikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ na pea otaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ pambeleme ekitaęž‰ hone na wilimime. Ikitaęž‰ natehali hao akaęž‰ na yameke pa tia hataęž‰ leke holu peleme.  
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki manaęž‰ alo ekitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taleke kolo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hambemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hamoko halo peleme tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo hakepiki akaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ piki pa tia haleeki aęž‰mbao yamoemenaęž‰ hambaęž‰pee. Kutupa handolo peleme tupaęž‰ mandane mulamula ikaęž‰ lekenaęž‰ liamenaęž‰ hambaęž‰pee.  
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ homolo wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ pimaęž‰ hando laa panisi peao halome. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ hoki walaęž‰pe.  
\v 20 Opuaęž‰pe. IĚ±taęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ kili kili lao halome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yaka pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opua potaęž‰ lombeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ipiki yaapo ne nolueke. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make IĚ± yaapo ne nelieke.  
\v 21 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mo yaka kini seanaęž‰ lopulao pitulupeke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ bepolaotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ yaka Apaęž‰naęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ lopulao pilupaęž‰ tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 22 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ mo siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ lo halaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 4  
\s1 Hepeni nane biki minaęž‰liaaso yeiyaęž‰ laasemeeki  
\p
\v 1 Koto natenaęž‰ kone ya nane oli hepeni potaęž‰ lombaęž‰pa wiaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hande ambaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi la kiaęž‰ bu kanakemaęž‰ handeke pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pate epoe laa Kutupa doeki hoki nane pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki waluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Koto kone mo Sipitidimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ e pokeaęž‰me. Oli hepeni nanetaęž‰ mo kilu tumbao pilaęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ manda pitiaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ yenki tieke yeke toopimanu diaęž‰sepa make kanilianimaęž‰ make leke yale yale pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeaęž‰me. Kutupa mo emulolidi toopinaęž‰ au leke kaęž‰laęž‰daęž‰peiya mo kilu tumbao pilaęž‰eki popei yao wiekeeki handoaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Mo hande kini sea popei yaotaęž‰ mandane hali tieke homekenaęž‰ tonkopu kini seamanu wiaęž‰me. Moeki manunaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali tieke homekenaęž‰ tonkopu you haliweki hake piki dau yamaataęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki handeteke halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ you akaęž‰manu pambaememe.  
\v 5 Mo kini sea paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ ti tekelemanu make aęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ piki tutu make mo tutu tieke litaęž‰laęž‰eki make yapeaęž‰me. Mo kini seanaęž‰ puki tikitikitaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ olaęž‰pakemanu talo hayaęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ watake hataęž‰ sipitidimanu yaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa mo kini seanaęž‰ puki nane ombutaęž‰ kalasimaęž‰ handeke alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taleke hamaęž‰ tieke wiaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me.  
\p Mo kini seanaęž‰ nepoko ninaęž‰taęž‰ pa deto hao halaęž‰ tonkopu alemanu ikaęž‰ puki nane make hoki nane paeyao lekemaęž‰ tumbiki ale manumaęž‰ popei yao wiaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Titinaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo bosikasi tieke biki laeonomaęž‰ handeaęž‰me. Yaapo peao ekitaęž‰ mo kao hali ekimaęž‰ handeaęž‰me. Tepo peao ekitaęž‰ halinaęž‰ leke popeleke hayaęž‰me. Tonko peao ekitaęž‰ bitutu laa pominaęž‰laęž‰ uda tiekemaęž‰ handeaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Mo deto halaęž‰ alemanu homeke homekemaęž‰taęž‰ watake hataęž‰ popake haememe. Kutupa ikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ oto nane make hamaęž‰ nane make lekemaęž‰ tumbulu bao wiaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ peliolo da kaęž‰laęž‰polo tombo na wiki lo haleme emelitaęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Tekehali Aneke Kodaęž‰taęž‰ yako piki yako piki yako piki Kodaęž‰o.  
\q1 Ambaęž‰ make hayaęž‰ ame make halaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ make halo paęž‰laęž‰ halie laa lo halememe.   
\p
\v 9 Mo deto haleme tonkopu ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ hoto paeyao pa hao halo paęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki keiyae alaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ emelimanu lo halememe. Kutupu haleme dinaęž‰taęž‰  
\v 10 mo hali tieke homekenaęž‰ tonkopu you haliwekitaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ hoto paeyao pa hao halo paęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao lopaataęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lo halememe. Ikaęž‰ you akaęž‰manu mo kini seanaęž‰ puki tikitiki lopaaso dupa lo halememe.   
\q1
\v 11 Nikaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰o. Neke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki make yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki make honkopu make anaęž‰naęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao waęž‰peleme. Kutupa nakaęž‰ hone pi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hapekeeki make daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki make halaęž‰me laa lo halememe.   
\c 5  
\s1 Pi ulaęž‰ buka pitaęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ halinaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰ buka miniki pitiaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. Mo pi ulaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ nepoko yaapo telipunaęž‰taęž‰ wapemaęž‰ tumbulu bao wiaęž‰me. Kutupa watake hataęž‰ tonkaake alemaęž‰ tonkaeyekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa wele wopu piki enisolo handoaęž‰me. Mo enisolomaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tiekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo tonkaake alemanu yambaęž‰la mo pi ulaęž‰ buka lumbuluekemaęž‰ epitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe leaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Pate oli hepeni nane make do kenke nane make kenke oto nane make mo pi ulaęž‰ buka lumba tukiki nane handaęž‰peke some maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me.  
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰ kaęž‰paęž‰puki yoka eĚ± tieke loaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo pi ulaęž‰ bukataęž‰ lumba tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰peke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo hande you hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ EĚ± na lapee. Handaęž‰e. Hande Diudanaęž‰ tapake laeonotaęž‰ hande Deipidinaęž‰ eiyekemaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pea aęž‰pa otaęž‰ biki wiki hali mendieke somemaęž‰ homeke bepolao halaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ tonkaakemanu ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰la mo pi ulaęž‰ buka lumbaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki homeketaęž‰ mo kini sea tukikinaęž‰ hayaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ ale tonkopu make mo you haliwekimaęž‰ make dupaememe. Mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikitaęž‰ limiki nono piekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ ekekemanu hao make watake hataęž‰ lekemanu hayaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ leke manutaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ watake hataęž‰ sipitidimanu do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalaęž‰eki yekeme.  
\v 7 Mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ halinaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ wia pitiaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ buka pua miaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Dupitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ tonkopu ale manumaęž‰ make mo hali tieke homekenaęž‰ tonkopu you haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ puki tikitikinaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao lopememe. Homeke homekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo kidamaęž‰ handeke ale make mo kolomaęž‰ wepiki ulu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ totopo piki alemaęž‰ tumbikieki wimime. Kototaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yekeme.  
\v 9 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ panake emeli homeke alotaęž‰  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰ buka mea tonkaake ale yambaęž‰lapeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke neketaęž‰ limikime. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haenaęž‰yeke hambeleme.  
\q1 Ikitaęž‰ tapake taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make kapomani manumaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make tutu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hambeleme.   
\q1
\v 10 Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo yeni peao halaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki haenaęž‰yeke Kodaęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰ leleme.  
\q1 Ikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ lelipikie laa lemekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Pa handoeketaęž‰ mo yataęž‰peaęž‰peke na yeke tupaęž‰ haemeke enisolo tititaęž‰ daoseni eleke eleke opuaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ mo kini sea make mo deto halaęž‰ tonkopu alemanu make mo you haliweki popei yao haememe.  
\v 12 Kutupa pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make anekemaęž‰ emeli alo alotaęž‰  
\q1 Mo hande liaęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰taęž‰ wele make  
\q1 hamoko make hone u tiaasaęž‰eki make honkopu make  
\q1 biki miniliaasaęž‰eki make paĚ±aĚ± pikieki make  
\q1 yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki make paeyao meaęž‰peketaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Kutupa oli ya nane make kenkenaęž‰ make kenke oto nane make dawala paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta halaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ emeli lemeeki opuaęž‰me. Dupa lememe.  
\q1 Mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ hali make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki make  
\q1 yeiyaęž‰ lao make biki miniliao make paĚ±aĚ± make wele make  
\q1 hoto paeyao pa u haenaęž‰e lememe.   
\p
\v 14 Koto lemeke mo deto halaęž‰ tonkopu ale manumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutu pinaęž‰e lemeke mo you haliwekitaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao lopa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laaso yeni pimime.   
\c 6  
\s1 Tonkaake alemanu  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ tonkaake ale homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰peeke handoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo deto halaęž‰ tonkopu ale homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ tutu liki nono pea alotaęž‰ Epoe leeki opuaęž‰me.  
\v 2 IĚ±maęž‰ handoeketaęž‰ handetaęž‰ hakepiki hosi maęž‰naęž‰ yekeme. Mo maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitieke halimaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndeli miniki pitiaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ you akaęž‰ haleaęž‰me. Kutu pieke ipikitaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ bepolalo poluekemaęž‰ pulaęž‰ hali tupaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pita peaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ hande yaapo peao tonkaake ale kaęž‰laęž‰peaaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ ale yaapo peao ekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epoe leaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ wepiki hosi maęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰me. Mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitieke halitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hali yankeke ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lu alu alu pinaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki mea epenaęž‰yeke honkopu haleaęž‰me. Kutupa make bainasi tieke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ haleaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 5 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ mo tepo peao tonkaake ale kaęž‰laęž‰peaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ ale tepo peao ekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epoe leaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ handoeketaęž‰ handetaęž‰ punupiki hosi maęž‰naęž‰ yekeme. Koto hosi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hoki manda pitieke halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tombo mu halaęž‰ ale miniaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Hande deto halaęž‰ tonkopu alemanu haeme ale tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ leke nono pea alotaęž‰ Nate homekenaęž‰ e pokaa minaęž‰laęž‰ yenkimaęž‰taęž‰ widi putu piliki siki homeke hambenaęž‰ laa mo widimaęž‰ handeke ale balitaęž‰ tukikinaęž‰ putupaa homeke yenkimaęž‰ kone hambenaęž‰e. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo olipi timanu make waini emanu make na hoeyaapaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ tonko peao tonkaake ale kaęž‰laęž‰peaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo tonko peao deto halaęž‰ alemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epoe leaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Handoeketaęž‰ handetaęž‰ hamipiki hosi maęž‰naęž‰ yekeme. Mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ manda pitieke halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Homaęž‰laęž‰eki leaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ mo homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ temoko halaęž‰ kenketaęž‰ teliaęž‰ mea teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu hayaęž‰me. Ipilikitaęž‰ do kenke tonkopu tekilipa homeke homeke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make teaęž‰ ki make yeni ki make hapekenaęž‰ halaęž‰ yeti sayale manumaęž‰ make paeyao linaęž‰yeke honkopu haleaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ yunki peao tonkaake ale kaęž‰laęž‰peaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaaso hataęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke walaemeke handa limiki haliwekinaęž‰ temokomanu mo oloda oto paęž‰taęž‰ wieke handoaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Koto temoko manumaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi alotaęž‰ Yako pea otaęž‰ hau pu hale wele wopu piki Tekehalio. Mo niki limi tapake panisi pealuekemaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali pi yokaalu pulu pele natetaęž‰ handimaęž‰pe lememe.  
\v 11 Mo haliweki homeke homeketaęž‰ hake piki dau hale hale pea alotaęž‰ Mo iki litolo piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ e pokeleme yankeke titi paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ lu paeyaenaęž‰ hosiki siki hoto pitaęž‰pee leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Kutupa mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ mo yunki mindiki hataęž‰ tonkaake ale kaęž‰laęž‰peeke handoaęž‰me. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰ piki yu momeni tieke pea mo natetaęž‰ da hokolo pupapeke akaęž‰ hankolakemaęž‰ handaataęž‰ mo kaisepotaęž‰ we au lolo yapeaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Mo hombulankaęž‰ manutaęž‰ mo hande kankake nose kiliki po tilipu tiekemaęž‰ tandelaęž‰ litaęž‰leke lopaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ oni kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa lopeaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Oli yataęž‰ mo hande keda tako pu minolo pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ alupaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa pote paeyao make dawalamaęž‰ popei yaalaęž‰ kenkemanu paeyaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hao halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ na hake ane mone pimime.  
\v 15 Kutupa do kenkenaęž‰ kinimanu make handeteke halaęž‰ haliweki make aminaęž‰ you haliweki make hamoko haliweki make wele wopu piki haliweki make pa hameke e pokaaseme haliweki make pa haleme haliweki make paeyao siki oni apaęž‰ndaęž‰ make pote paęž‰taęž‰manu ulaęž‰ toopi tieke tieke paęž‰taęž‰manu aęž‰mbao pitulu endi pimime.  
\v 16 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo potemanu make toopimanu paęž‰taęž‰ wi laęž‰ moneaaso alotaęž‰ Mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki aęž‰mbao niki manda aęž‰pa lopaęž‰pee.  
\v 17 Ipilikaęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke natetaęž‰ domaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ doeki mea baapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe lememe.   
\c 7  
\s1 144 daoseni Isulai wandaęž‰hali  
\p
\v 1 Doeki hoki nanetaęž‰ enisolo tonkopumaęž‰ mo kenke honiki tonkopu telipa haemeeki handoaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo tonkopu pomaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke make dawala make ti maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo pomaęž‰ tiaamaęž‰naęž‰ miniki haememe.  
\v 2 Kutupa enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tonkaake ale miniki hataęž‰ oli nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke pitaęž‰ ikali yaapo hoeyaenaęž‰yeke honkopu halaęž‰laęž‰ tonkopu enisolomanu paęž‰taęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi laęž‰ moneayaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Mo enisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki ikaęž‰ wenoko manunaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tombomaęž‰ maka u paeyaomaęž‰kaęž‰na mo kenke make dawala make mo timanu make hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ ame dotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na hoeyaapee leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Kutupa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kieketaęž‰ Mo Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tombomaęž‰ maka ulaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ 144 daoseni halememe leaęž‰me. Koto wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo hande Isulainaęž‰ 12 tapakee leaęž‰me.  
\v 5-8 Ikitaęž‰ 12 daoseni lo mo tapake homeke homeke paęž‰taęž‰ yataęž‰po maęž‰laęž‰me. Mo tapake biki manutaęž‰ Diuda Lubeni Kaęž‰daęž‰ Aęž‰sea Naęž‰petali Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ Simioni Lipae Isaka Sebuloni Diosepe make Benisamini koto tapake manue.   
\s1 Hone pa mataęž‰papeke tapake tieke  
\p
\v 9 Doeki hoki nanetaęž‰ hone pa mataęž‰papeke tapake tieke handoaęž‰me. Do wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yataęž‰peaęž‰peke tapake tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tutu paeyao make tapake paeyao make kapomani taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ kenke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make pi taęž‰taęž‰ leke tapake paeyao siki haememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ puki tikitikinaęž‰ hakepiki dau yama hau palo miniki haememe.  
\v 10 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ anekemaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Daęž‰taęž‰mono yeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰me lememe.   
\p
\v 11 Enisolo paeyaotaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ make mo you haliweki make mo deto halaęž‰ ale tonkopu paeyao popei yao hao yapememe. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ puki tikitikinaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao lopolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰  
\v 12 Kutu pinaęž‰e. Yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki make paĚ±aĚ± make hone u lenkene peaasaęž‰eki make taęž‰naęž‰e alaęž‰eki make biki miniliaasaęž‰eki make wele honkopu make paeyaotaęž‰ hoto paeyao nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki ulaęž‰me. Kutu pinaęž‰e lememe.   
\s1 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu paetaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 13 Mo halaęž‰ you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo hake piki dau yameleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ epi ameda kaęž‰taęž‰pe laataęž‰ hanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pelemepe leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Someo. IĚ± hone na ulupate nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hone wilime loaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ mo hande otaęž‰ hoke tanda paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kone epeke tupaęž‰ epeleme wandaęž‰halie leaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ akaęž‰ manutaęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ wemaęž‰ tandaęž‰pa hake peao pelememe.  
\v 15 Koto peleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ puki tikitikinaęž‰ hataęž‰ peliolo da kaęž‰laęž‰polo ipikaęž‰ tembolo paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokao halememe. Mo kini seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki handeteke pitilieke.  
\v 16 Ikitaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ make ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ make otaęž‰ paa na homilimikie. Kutupa make nate o ti ulekemaęž‰ potaasaęž‰ ale tupaęž‰ make na yankilieke.  
\v 17 Pa ekipeke mo kini sea tukikinaęž‰ halaęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali halieke. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kitaęž‰laęž‰ tunkulu pa pitumu pitumu paęž‰laęž‰ ikalimanu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pelieke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± pankekemanu paeyao honu baalieke.   
\c 8  
\s1 Watake peao tonkaake ale  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikimaęž‰ mo watake peao ale kelepeaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ oli hepeni nane nate leke awa homeke tukikinaęž‰ no laęž‰pa peaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutupa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ halaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ enisolomanu paęž‰taęž‰ watake hataęž‰ bu kanake haleaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki totopo piki ale yanko halaęž‰ kanake miniki mo oloda wiaęž‰ alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa hayaęž‰me. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yenimanu ameĚ±leĚ± totopo piki alemanu wopu apaęž‰taenaęž‰yeke haleaęž‰me. Koto ale manutaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ puki tikitiki ulaęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki olodanaęž‰ yankenaęž‰yeke piaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Mo totopopiki ale yankeaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lumutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni taapu mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ puki tikitiki halaęž‰ enisolonaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰meiya peaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa mo enisolomaęž‰ mo totopo piki ale pambaęž‰laęž‰ kanake mea mo olodanaęž‰ talo hayaęž‰ ti mea apaęž‰tao do kenkenaęž‰ wekilaęž‰ holaeyaęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰ tomonaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰piki tutu make tutu tieke make ti tekele make yu momeni make piaęž‰me.   
\s1 Bu kanake litaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu  
\p
\v 6 Koto kone mo watake hataęž‰ bu kanake miniki haeme watake hataęž‰ enisolo manumaęž‰ mo bu kanakemanu luekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao hao yapememe.   
\p
\v 7 Titinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ya hapeke pitaęž‰ ti uleke apaęž‰taake we ikali anekemaęž‰ doĚ±uĚ± hao oni kenkenaęž‰ lopeaęž‰me. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo kenketaęž‰ tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ timaęž‰ to paeyaęž‰me. Kutupa mo timanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ timaęž‰ to paeyaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ mo ambu paeyao siki taęž‰taęž‰ paeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Kutupa mo yaapo peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰me. Pote tieke hombeleke ti talo talo hake nono piki alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ oni dawala paęž‰taęž‰ holaeyaęž‰me. Mo dawala tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ we au lolo yapeaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mo dawala paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ alemanu tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ homeaęž‰me. Kutupa kawaso make homeke hau kone pea hoeyaeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa mo tepo peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰me. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo talo talo hake dosimaęž‰ handeke hombulankaęž‰ tieke ya nanemaęž‰ lopaęž‰niao mo ikali yopulaęž‰ ekimanu make opaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ manda lopeaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Mo hombulankaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Teto paęž‰laęž‰ekie. Kutupa mo ikali manutaęž‰ tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ teto piaęž‰me. Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ koto ikali no hao homememe. Pa ekipeke mo ikalitaęž‰ teto pitolo hataęž‰ piaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Kutupa mo tonkopu enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰me. Kutu pieketaęž‰ nate make kaisepo make hombulankaęž‰manu make tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ lu tondo peayaęž‰eki yaalo ikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ alupaememe. Kutupa mo natepataęž‰ tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± na piaęž‰me. Timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki make homeke hau kone piaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Kutupa handoaęž‰pate oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±eĚ±yaĚ± ida tieke anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰pee. Aęž‰pee. Mo mandane enisolo tepomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ekipiki tanda tieke piki kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu milimikipe.   
\c 9  
\s1 Yunki peao enisolonaęž‰ bu kanake  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo yunki peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰me. Hombulankaęž‰ homeke oni kenkenaęž‰ hondaęž‰pa lopeekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ mo honiki na wiki naku tieke kiakenaęž‰ potaęž‰ ki haleaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Mo hombulankaęž‰maęž‰ mo naku tieke kiakenaęž‰ potaęž‰ lombeaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ti tieke yankaęž‰leke opaęž‰laęž‰ lumumaęž‰ handeke lumu holaęž‰lu baeyaęž‰me. Mo lumumaęž‰taęž‰ nate make ya make timbaęž‰laęž‰ pamba hayaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Hombutaęž‰taęž‰ mo lumu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰pa oni kenkenaęž‰ lopememe. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ teihali manumaęž‰ haleme honkopumaęž‰ handeke honkopu haleaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo e alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ ambu make timanu make mandane ambumanu paeyao na hoeyaapaęž‰peke laataęž‰ hoeyaapeke ale homeketaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tombomaęž‰ maka ikaęž‰ wenokonaęž‰ na ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homeke hoeyaapaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo hombutaęž‰maęž‰ handeke ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali homenaęž‰yeke linaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa kaisepo yunki hataęž‰ natenaęž‰ homeke tanda tieke halolo ombu haenaęž‰ leaęž‰me. Mo tanda tieketaęž‰ mo teihalimaęž‰ pokaęž‰leke minaęž‰laęž‰ tanda tupaęž‰e.  
\v 6 Koto yunki hataęž‰ kaisepo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki weilimipate na handaęž‰ wilimikie. Homawee hone wilimipate homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pelieke.   
\p
\v 7 Mo hombutaęž‰ tititaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao halaęž‰ hosi maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ handememe. Ikaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰taęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki you akaęž‰maęž‰ handeke ale pambao ikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ halinaęž‰ leke popelekemaęž‰ handeaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Ikaęž‰ itikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰wekinaęž‰ hokulupiki itikimaęž‰ handaa ikaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ laeononaęž‰ kakemaęž‰ handeaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Ikaęž‰ hakokotaęž‰ ayenimaęž‰ wepiki hakokonaęž‰ yamaęž‰laęž‰ alemaęž‰ handeke ekimaęž‰ tote pea kutupa ikaęž‰ popakemaęž‰ laeme eĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ polukumaęž‰ ipupula yopulaęž‰ hosi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ aielaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰ka mendekemanu yopulu leke nono piaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Ikitaęž‰ mendeke hao teihalinaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ tekeke haememe. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kaisepo yunki hataęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ mendekemaęž‰ tanda halo paęž‰laęž‰ honkopu haememe.  
\v 11 Kini homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki handeteke halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo honiki na wiki naku tieke kiakenaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ enisoloe. Hibulu pimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aęž‰baęž‰dono. Kitiki pimaęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰poliyono Koto bikitaęž‰ Hoeyaasaęž‰ halie laa alaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Titinaęž‰ paalaęž‰piki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieketaęž‰ koto paelaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Doeki hoki nanetaęž‰ paalaęž‰piki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke yaapo epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki pa ulaęž‰me.   
\s1 Yunki mindiki peao enisolonaęž‰ bu kanake  
\p
\v 13 Kutupa mo yunki mindiki peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰me. Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ puki tikitiki hayaęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki olodanaęž‰ nepoko tonkopu nanemaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make epeaęž‰eki opuaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Mo pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ mo yunki mindiki peao enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Yupoteitisi ikali tieke paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaalaęž‰ enisolo tonkopu kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapae leaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Mo enisolomanu kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ do awa siki make otaęž‰ do nate siki make otaęž‰ do kaisepo siki make otaęž‰ do bapi siki make epenaęž‰yeke wialaęž‰ natenaęž‰ linaęž‰yeke tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Mo wandaęž‰hali lulu polo pieke hosi hokinaęž‰ pitieke ami tapakenaęž‰ nambataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ 200 milioni haliweki leaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutupa yaka upamaęž‰ leke handoaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ make ikaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitimi haliweki handoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo haliwekinaęž‰ hakokonaęž‰ yameleme alenaęž‰ au laęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo ti lankakemaęž‰ handa we pupa pua make oli ya punupaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeke toopi saęž‰paeyanaęž‰ au lekeeki make mo hami pupapeke toopi solopanaęž‰ au lekeeki make au leaęž‰me. Mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ amboketaęž‰ laeononaęž‰ ambokemaęž‰ handaa ikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ti uleke make lumu make ti na honi papeke lankake biki solopa opolu baeyaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Do ki yeni leke litaęž‰laęž‰ hau tepomaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ homo paeyaęž‰me. Mo hosinaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ opolu baeyaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ make mendeke paęž‰taęž‰manu ulaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ mendeke manutaęž‰ amboke hake ketomaęž‰ handeaęž‰me. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tanda peao haememe.   
\p
\v 20 Do hau tepomaęž‰ na liaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wepia wia yeni pu haeme ale paęž‰taęž‰manu hoki na walememe. Ikitaęž‰ mo hoke temoko titi paęž‰taęž‰ make mo kolomaęž‰ make silipamaęž‰ make toopimaęž‰ make timaęž‰ make toopi ti wepia wimiki alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki hoki na walememe. Mo handaęž‰peke na yeke make pi na opuaęž‰peke make pi na lapeke ale manunaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Kutupa make ikaęž‰ hali homenaęž‰ lilimieki make ikaęž‰ tiĚ±oĚ± haumanu make ikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu make pake nalaęž‰ ekimanu kone otaęž‰ na kiaememe.   
\c 10  
\s1 Enisolo pitaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ buka hosikale siki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa wele wopu piki enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰nialo epeeke handoaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ koamaęž‰ ambula bao ipikaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰daęž‰peiyamaęž‰ ambula wiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ natemaęž‰ handaa ipikaęž‰ anketaęž‰ ti talo talo hake da pinki manumaęž‰ handeekeme.  
\v 2 Ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰taęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ buka hosiki ale siki lumbu wia hayaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ popeke nane anketaęž‰ dawala manda wia ipikaęž‰ hoe nane anketaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ wia hayaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Kutupa laeono manunaęž‰ aneke eĚ± wi alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi leaęž‰me. Mo wi leaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ tutu manumaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi laa hombo peaememe.  
\v 4 Mo pi leaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ kone IĚ±taęž‰ wape laanialuekemaęž‰ pitono oli hepeni nane pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do watake hataęž‰ tutu manumaęž‰ lemeke ekitaęž‰ na laaniake aęž‰mbaapeke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 5-6 Mo hande dawala pitaęž‰ kenke yaapo manda hayeke handoaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ do kenke ya make dawala make koto paęž‰taęž‰manu halaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ make koto ale paeyaonaęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ hoto paeyao pa hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Nate yolaęž‰ moneapeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 7 pa mo watake hataęž‰ peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ potopede haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ la haleeke tupaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pulueke laa aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pu paeyaalieke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Kutupa oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ hande IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi laa kiaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make ombumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo dawala make kenke yaapo manda halaęž‰ enisolonaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ lumba wia halaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ buka pua mie leaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± pua mo enisolo lotaęž‰ pitolotaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰ hosiki buka siki kie loaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mea nae. Neliaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ weleke nolo paęž‰laęž‰pate nakaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ boi hapekemaęž‰ handaa tende yole pilieke leaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Koto leeke IĚ±maęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰ hosiki buka siki mea noaęž‰pate boi hapekemaęž‰ handaa tende yole piaęž‰me. Pate neliawaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ yaka weleke neaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 11 Kutupa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo kapomanimanu handeteke pilaęž‰ kenke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make tutu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make kini taęž‰taęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi tapaasaęž‰eki paa lawaapekee leaęž‰me.   
\c 11  
\s1 Mo wekitisi yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tombo minaęž‰laęž‰ alemaęž‰ handeke tolo kitolo alotaęž‰ Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tembolo da make mo oloda yaapo pua tombo mie laataęž‰ mo tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piteleme wandaęž‰hali yataęž‰peaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Pate mo hamaęž‰ nane mombaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ hamaęž‰ manutaęž‰ tombo na miaęž‰pe leaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke koto ekitaęž‰ mo pi na miniki haleme tapake paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ hamaęž‰e leaęž‰me. Koto tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ kaisepo halitieke yaaponaęž‰ paa yaaponaęž‰ mo yakopiki daoni lu tumbalimikie.  
\v 3 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ yaka wekitisi hali yaapo mo palaowamanu mondu halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ dau yamao 1 daoseni kutupa 260 natemanu Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walawaenaęž‰ tapaalueke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Mo wekitisi hali yaapotaęž‰ mo olipi ti yaapo pitaęž‰ olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ ale yaapoe. Ipilikitaęž‰ mo kenke Tekehalinaęž‰ puki tikitiki halepeme.  
\v 5 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ koto hali yaapo hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ti uleke ipilikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ opolu bao mo ipilikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki haliweki hoeyaalieke. Kutupa dupilipi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ taapilimi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ lilieke.  
\v 6 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laaso halipi natenaęž‰ lako na epenaęž‰ laa oli ya aęž‰mbolotaęž‰ honkopu ulaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo opolo halaęž‰ ikali manutaęž‰ we au lenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ make ane mone yeni ki ipilikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ do kenke aęž‰pa hoeyaenaęž‰ laa make honkopu ulaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ pi walo paeyaalipi natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo honiki na wiki naku tieke kiake paęž‰taęž‰ hao opulu baaliaęž‰ sayalemaęž‰ handeke ale tieke hombelekemaęž‰ mo hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilieke. Mo alemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo bepolao lu homaotaęž‰  
\v 8 ipilikaęž‰ tokotaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ Tekehali lu endiaemeke daoni tiekenaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ pa winaęž‰ lelieke. Koto daonitaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ alaęž‰ biki yaapotaęž‰ Sodomo pitaęž‰ Idiepi yaapo ulaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Kapomani taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ kenkemanu make tapake taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ make pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ make tutu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ make paeyaomaęž‰ mo hali yaaponaęž‰ tokotaęž‰ nate teponaęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ handolo make na hoinaęž‰ lelimikie.  
\v 10 Pa ekipeke do kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo homelepe ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie. Kutupa ne pambolo hataęž‰ pa halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone anemone tapa alu alu pilimikie. Pa ekipeke mo potopede hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tanda tieke mea epepeme laa lelimikie.   
\p
\v 11 Koto nate tepo paeya nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰ pomo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰pa mo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeeketaęž‰ mo hali yaapo tialu pipime. Kutupa mo hali yaapo handeme wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homememe.  
\v 12 Mo potopede hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ oli ya nane pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tiekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pate ipupe leaęž‰me. Kutupa ipilikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handaęž‰paęž‰lia haenaęž‰ mo hali yaapotaęž‰ koa piti oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ pepeme.  
\v 13 Koto konetaęž‰ yumomeni tieke pea mo daonitaęž‰ kiki yaapo tekili pea homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ hoeyao mo daoseni watake hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homememe. Kutupa mo pa haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ moeki handolo hataęž‰ pututumaęž‰ homolo oli hepeni halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aneke ekinaęž‰ biki minaęž‰liaememe.   
\p
\v 14 Yaapo peao hoeyaasaęž‰ hau koto paeyaęž‰pate mo tepo peao hoeyaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipilieke.   
\s1 Watake hataęž‰ peao bu kanake  
\p
\v 15 Kutupa mo watake hataęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bu kanake liaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ oli hepeni nane pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tieke tieke manumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo kenke handeteke halo paęž‰laęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ ametaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ hali Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Kutupa hoto paeyao handeteke hao halieke lememe.  
\v 16 Kutupa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ puki tikitikinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ pitimi hande halitieke homekenaęž‰ tonkopu you haliwekitaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰   
\q1
\v 17 Ambaęž‰ pa hao hae make ame make hale Aneke Tekehali Kodaęž‰o.  
\q1 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wele tieke mea ametaęž‰ kini pea handeteke hale ekinaęž‰ keiyae alomaęž‰me laa alotaęž‰   
\q1
\v 18 Mo pi na miniki haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mineke pankelememe. Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mineke pankele natetaęž‰ opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu peleme nate aęž‰paęž‰leke loaęž‰me.  
\q1 Kutupa make nakaęž‰ e pokaeyaęž‰ potopede haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yenki seliapo halo pele aneke nate aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo neke paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ homu pea haleme wandaęž‰hali otaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ nate make loaęž‰me.  
\q1 Do kenke hoeyaaseme wandaęž‰hali hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ nate opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa lememe.   
\p
\v 19 Oli hepeni nane halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tembolotaęž‰ lumbiaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hande pi laęž‰ wiekeeki wieke bokosi handoaęž‰me. Kutupa ti tekele make aęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ piki tutu make tutu tiekemanu make yumomeni make ya hapeke wopu make epeaęž‰me.   
\c 12  
\s1 Mo wandaęž‰ pitaęž‰ popake itiki hake si handeke ale tieke yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pea hone mateke hau tieke oli yanaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰ homeke koto paęž‰taęž‰ pitiaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ dautaęž‰ mo nate yameaęž‰me. Kutupa mo kaisepotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ wia kutupa ipikaęž‰ you akaęž‰taęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo hombulankaęž‰ pambaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ipikitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ weki mulu puaęž‰peke yataęž‰ mo weki hoki neaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ tanda tieke pitolo hataęž‰ eĚ± wi leaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰piki ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ oli ya manda opolo epeaęž‰me. Handetaęž‰ we pupapeke popake itiki hake simaęž‰ handeke ale tieke hombeleke ipikaęž‰ amboketaęž‰ paeyao watake hataęž‰ hao kutupa kiki yaapo ekeke hayaęž‰me. Kutupa mo ambokemanu yalaotaęž‰ kininaęž‰ you akaęž‰ pamba pamba piaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Ipikaęž‰ mendekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hombulankaęž‰manu tepo tekilipa homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo ya minaęž‰paęž‰lao yola yopua do kenkenaęž‰ wekilaęž‰ lopaeyaęž‰me. Mo aletaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ weki mondu lopaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ mea nolueke alo puki tikitiki pua hayaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hali weki mondu wiaęž‰me. Ipiki daeyaataęž‰ do kenke paeyao ayeni dopitamaęž‰ handeteke halo paęž‰laęž‰ wekie. Pate mo wekitaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ mea peaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amu pea wiaęž‰yeke hapupapeke alenaęž‰ pindipa peaęž‰me. Koto alenaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ daoseni homeke kutupa 260 natenaęž‰ handeteke halo piaęž‰ alenaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 7 Kutupa oli hepeni nane aęž‰ndaęž‰ kini piaęž‰me. Maikolo ipikaęž‰ enisolo ameĚ±leĚ± mo popake itiki hake si ipikaęž‰ enisolo ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimime.  
\v 8 Pate Maikolo tapakemaęž‰ mo popake itiki hake sitaęž‰ bepolao ipikaęž‰ enisolomanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hepeni na haenaęž‰ lememe.  
\v 9 Mo popake itiki hake si tieke hombeleketaęž‰ tolu lopaeyaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ kiake hayeke keto biki Sadani laęž‰laęž‰ alee. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao makeaeyeke halie. Ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo titi ameĚ±leĚ± oni kenkenaęž‰ tolu lopaeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa oli hepeni nane pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tiekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ niki daęž‰taęž‰monoyeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki ta aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e. Ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipiki kini hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weletaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Ametaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰eki peneme yao walaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ puki tikitikinaęž‰ hataęž‰ peliolo da kelepolo nikaęž‰ kamemanu maĚ±leke lia hokeeki paęž‰laęž‰me lo hayaęž‰ halitaęž‰ oli hepeni minaęž‰paęž‰lao tolu lopaalaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ wemaęž‰ make mo otaęž‰ ekie laa waleme ekimaęž‰ make bepolayaęž‰me. Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pinaęž‰ pa hoeyao homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa pulumeke laa lememe.  
\v 12  Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ oli hepeni make koto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰halio paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰pee. Pate oni dawala pitaęž‰ kenke yaapotaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke hande Sadanitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ hosiki nate lekesiki homeke ulaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Mo popake itiki hake si tieke hombelekemaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo kenke nane tolu lopaalaęž‰me hone wiaataęž‰ mo hande weki mondu wiaęž‰ wandaęž‰ minuluekemaęž‰yeke teliolo ombu hayaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da mo hapupapeke alenaęž‰ penaęž‰yeketaęž‰ ida tiekenaęž‰ popake yaapo haleaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo popake itiki hake simaęž‰ hoeyaapaęž‰naęž‰ bapi teponaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ kaiseponaęž‰ handeteke halo piaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰e.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo popake itiki hake simaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeaęž‰ ikali wopumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ teliaęž‰ mea penaęž‰ leaęž‰me. Handetaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ ikali naa homenaęž‰yeke piaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Kutu piaęž‰pate kenkemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake aĚ±aĚ± laa mo popake itiki hake sinaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰ ikali mea neliayaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutu piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo popake itiki hake si tieke hombelekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mineke tieke pankolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pulu peaęž‰me. Koto tapaketaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua Yesumaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke hone tu laeme wandaęž‰halie.  
\v 18 Kutupa mo popake itiki hake sitaęž‰ dawala hounaęž‰ tiao hayaęž‰me.   
\c 13  
\s1 Sayale yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo sayale hombeleketaęž‰ mo dawala paęž‰taęž‰ pita opolo epeaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. Mo aletaęž‰ ekeke kiki yaapo hao amboke watake hataęž‰ hayaęž‰me. Mo ekekemanu yalaotaęž‰ kini you akaęž‰ pambamaęž‰ pambamaęž‰ piaęž‰me. Kutupa mo amboke manunaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ kitaake biki laememe.  
\v 2 Mo sayale hombeleketaęž‰ bosikasi tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki lepadimaęž‰ handaa ipikaęž‰ anketaęž‰ peiolomaęž‰ handeke ale tieke hombelekenaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ handaa ipikaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ laeononaęž‰ kakemaęž‰ handeaęž‰me. Mo hande popake itiki hake si tiekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honkopu make ipikaęž‰ kini sea make ipikaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰eki tieke paeyao mo sayale hombeleke paęž‰taęž‰ haleaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Mo sayalenaęž‰ amboke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ homenaęž‰ tupaęž‰ apaęž‰laęž‰ pokeekepate pa mea epeayeke handaa mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ penkili putia pominolo hataęž‰ mo sayale hombeleke teliaęž‰ mea pememe.  
\v 4 Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ mo popake itiki hake si paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pimime. Pa ekipeke mo simaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honkopu tieketaęž‰ mo sayale paęž‰taęž‰ haleeke handa loaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ sayale paęž‰taęž‰ make pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰ Epitaęž‰ mo sayalemaęž‰ handelemepe. Epimaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ honkopu aneke halaęž‰pe lememe.   
\p
\v 5 Mo sayalemaęž‰taęž‰ kaisepo hali tieke yaaponaęž‰ pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ hakoko litaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ kitaenaęž‰yeke waleke haleaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Mo sayalemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ biki make ipiki halaęž‰ da make oli hepeni haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao make yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homao hoeyaasaęž‰ pi kini pea leaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolaenaęž‰ make tapake taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make kapomani taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make tutu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make paeyao handeteke haenaęž‰ waleke haleaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Do kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo sayale paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pilimikie. Pate do kenke aĚ±iĚ± na wepiki haenaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ laalaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homeke homekemaęž‰ kotoeki na pilimikie. Koto biki ulaęž‰ bukataęž‰ hande limiki Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ bukae.   
\p
\v 9 Haleke haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 10 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mininaęž‰e laa wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ mininaęž‰ lelieke. Epitaęž‰ bainasimaęž‰ lia homaenaęž‰e laa wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo bainasimaęž‰ lia homaenaęž‰ lelieke. Dupiki haumanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali lopaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke homu pea pa pinaęž‰e laa yu wia hataęž‰ make kimaęž‰ na homeke hone tu lao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke.   
\p
\v 11 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo sayale hombeleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ mo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ opaęž‰liaeyeke handoaęž‰me. Do sayaletaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ ekekemaęž‰ handeke ekeke yaapo hayaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo popake itiki hake simaęž‰ alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Mo alemaęž‰taęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ sayalenaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰eki tieke meataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ e wopu pokeaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do kenke make do kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao make mo ambaęž‰ hande titinaęž‰ amboke hoeyaeyaęž‰pate paa epeaęž‰ sayale paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pipee laa honkopu wopu hao sutiaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Mo yaapo peao sayalemaęž‰taęž‰ na handeke haumanu wopu pitolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ ti uleke do kenkenaęž‰ lopenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ sayalenaęž‰ hau peaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ mokoto na handeke haumanu piaęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao makeaaso hataęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea peaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande bainasimaęž‰ hoeyaeyaęž‰pate pa tiao halaęž‰ titinaęž‰ sayale yeiyaęž‰ laaluekemaęž‰ koto ekimaęž‰ handekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ wepiaęž‰pe leaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo yaapo peao sayalemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande titinaęž‰ sayale mandaęž‰ meao wepimi ale paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ pomo halenaęž‰yeke waleke haleaęž‰me. Kutupiki hautaęž‰ mo alemaęž‰ pi lenaęž‰ la make mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ lapeke kiaalimi wandaęž‰hali paeyao lu homaenaęž‰yeke piaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 16 Mo yaapo peao sayalemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hosiki wandaęž‰hali make aneke wandaęž‰hali make hamoko wandaęž‰hali make natehali wandaęž‰hali make pa hameke e pokaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make pa haleme wandaęž‰hali make paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ o ikaęž‰ wenokonaęž‰taęž‰ maka maęž‰ndaęž‰ taĚ±laenaęž‰yeke honkopu hao sutiaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do maka na taĚ±laeyeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰manu otaęž‰ na hambo make tapao pinaęž‰e leaęž‰me. Koto makataęž‰ mo sayalenaęž‰ biki tapaęž‰ wiao o ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ namba haleke ekie.  
\v 18 Do ekimanu opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epeke hone u lenkene pitaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ epeke honemaęž‰ tumba wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto sayalenaęž‰ namba lo yokenaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke mo nambataęž‰ halinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ anketeke minolo kone laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto nambataęž‰ 666 laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 14  
\s1 Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali  
\p
\v 1 Kutupakaęž‰naęž‰ handoaęž‰pate mo hande Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ biki make ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰naęž‰ biki ikaęž‰ wenokonaęž‰ laemeke 144 daoseni wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mo Saioni potenaęž‰ haememe.  
\v 2 Kutupa oli ya nanemaęž‰ ikali doĚ±uĚ± tiekemaęž‰ handa make tutu tieke liki nonopiki pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opuaęž‰me. Mo pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maketaęž‰ kidamaęž‰ handeke ale litaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ liki nonopiki alaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeke nono piaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Mo 144 daoseni wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ make mo deto halaęž‰ tonkopu ale manunaęž‰ make mo you haliwekinaęž‰ puki tikitiki pua haememe. Ikitaęž‰ panake emeli ikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke mokaęž‰la hande hande pea lapeke emeli homeke lememe. Kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ koto tapake homeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea epeaalo piaęž‰ tapakee.  
\v 4 Ikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki hakopu na tunkulimieki yaalo yakopiki haliweki haememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki peaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ telipaleke ombu haememe. Ikitaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ epeaalaęž‰ tapakee. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki paęž‰taęž‰ make titinaęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ tapakee.  
\v 5 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yayapiki pi lelemeeki na opua make alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ na pealeme haliwekie.   
\s1 Enisolo tepo  
\p
\v 6 Kutupa enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ oli ya manda aĚ±eĚ±nolo hataęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mo pa u halaęž‰ Pi Seliapo laluekemaęž‰ piaęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ tutu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make tapake taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ make kapomani eleke elekemaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ kenke make paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ pieke handoaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tieke halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ biki minaęž‰liape. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰hali pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate aęž‰paęž‰leke loaęž‰me. Do kenke make oli ya make dawala make opaęž‰laęž‰ ikalimanu make koto ale paeyao waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni peaęž‰paęž‰peke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Kotoeki hoki nanetaęž‰ enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ teliolo alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰me. Aneke Baęž‰bilonitaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ipikaęž‰ waini ikali nenaęž‰ leaęž‰me. Mo honkopu hake waini ikalitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hoke hone paęž‰laęž‰eki manue leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Pa tepo peao enisolomaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰eki yaapo teliolo hataęž‰ anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo sayale hombeleke make koto ale mandaęž‰ meao waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ make pandaęž‰puniao yeni pitolo o ipikaęž‰ maka wenoko o popeke nane kikinaęž‰ taĚ±lenaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰  
\v 10 koto sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰naęž‰ waini ikali nelieke. Kotaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paalaęž‰piki mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ wele pa ulaęž‰ waini ikalitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ kapo paęž‰taęž‰ holo pambeekeeki loaęž‰me. Dupiliaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ mo yakopiki enisolo titi make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ leke tomonaęž‰ mo ti uleke make mo titipu tiekepiki lankaęž‰maęž‰ handeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ tanda no halimikie.  
\v 11 Mo tanda halo halaęž‰ tinaęž‰ lumutaęž‰ na paeyeke hoto paeyao pa u halieke. Koto sayale hombeleke pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mandaęž‰ meao waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ale yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pitolo make o koto alenaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ maka winaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ tanda no halo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nate o timbaęž‰ otaęž‰ hosiki siki na paeyaalieke leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Koto yaęž‰leke handaa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke hone tulao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali lopaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ pa pinaęž‰e laa yu wia halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ pilieke.   
\p
\v 13 Kutupa oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Doeki laaniae. Ame do kini pea mo Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokolo hataęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰me. Koto leeke mo Sipitidimaęž‰ hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ki hone na wiki honkopu hao pokelemeeki paeyaemeke handaa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ e pokeleme ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pa halaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\s1 Kenkenaęž‰ ne napeke minaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 14 Kutupa handoaęž‰pate ya hapi handoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo ya hapi mandaataęž‰ halimaęž‰ handeke ale pitiaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰taęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki kininaęž‰ you akaęž‰ pambao kutupa widi tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ ne wopu hake kaiya miniaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Kutupa mo enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰pa mo ya hapi manda pitiaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± wi tieke laęž‰moneaaso alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ widi tunkulu hale kaiyamaęž‰ ne napeke mie. Pa ekipeke mo natetaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa kenkenaęž‰ ne napeke minaęž‰ potaęž‰leke loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Koto leeke mo ya hapi manda pitiaęž‰ somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ widi tunkulu halaęž‰ kaiya wankeaaso hataęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ ne napeke mu paeyaeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 17 Kutupa enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ mo tembolo paęž‰taęž‰ pita opolu bao ipulu ne wopu hake kaiya ombu miniki epeaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kutupa mo tinaęž‰ handeteke hayaęž‰ enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo oloda paęž‰taęž‰ hao epeaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ne wopu hake kaiya miniki hayaęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ anekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kaiyamaęž‰ mo waini punaęž‰ kilikimanu hondaęž‰ pokaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke mo kiliki manutaęž‰ potaęž‰leke loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Kotaęž‰ mo enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kaiya do kenkenaęž‰ wankeaaso hataęž‰ mo waini kiliki manutaęž‰ talo pamba oni Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paalaęž‰ piki mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ waini kiliki dekepo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lopaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Mo waini kilikitaęž‰ mo daoni tieke hamaęž‰ nane mo waini kiliki dekepo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ dekepeaęž‰me. Kutupa mo dekepeaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ we ikali tieke 300 kilomida hokulu taa hataęž‰ otaęž‰ kendo tieke make mo hosinaęž‰ kake anaęž‰naęž‰ lombei peaęž‰peke kendo wiaęž‰me.   
\c 15  
\s1 Ane mone ke handaasaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ haumanu ipulaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa oli yanaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piki hone mateke pututu au tieke handoaęž‰me. Watake hataęž‰ enisolo manumaęž‰ paeyaaso ane mone ke handaasaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ haumanu miniki haememe. Kototaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paeyaaso mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki walo paeyaasaęž‰eki yekeme.   
\p
\v 2 Kutupa mo kalasimaęž‰ handeke hamaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ti uleke apaęž‰taakeeki handoaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hande sayale hombeleke make koto ale mandaęž‰ meao wepimiki sayale make mo alenaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ taapaęž‰ wiao laęž‰laęž‰ namba make bepolao haleme wandaęž‰hali handoaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ mo kalasi hamaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ tilao hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ kidamaęž‰ handeke alemanu miniki hataęž‰  
\v 3 mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokeeke hali Mosesinaęž‰ emeli make mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ emeli make lememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Aneke Tekehali Kodaęž‰o.  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ peao make yole make paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Tapake paeyaonaęž‰ kinio.  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ pitele haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ tikitiki pea otaęž‰ hau manue.   
\q1
\v 4 Tekehali neketaęž‰ epimaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homiliaęž‰pe.  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ hau tieke laaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ epimaęž‰ kiaaliaęž‰pe.  
\q1 Neke homeke homeke yako peleme.  
\q1 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pilimikie.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke nakaęž‰ yakopiki hau manutaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ ambaęž‰ handelememe lememe.   
\p
\v 5 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ oli hepeni nane mo tembolo da potaęž‰ lumba wiekeeki handoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo da tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± pi lo hayeke palai da handoaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Mo watake hataęž‰ enisolo manutaęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ ke handaęž‰peke ekimanu miniki hataęž‰ tembolo paęž‰taęž‰ hao epememe. Ikitaęž‰ hake piki leke yale yale piki dau yama kolomaęž‰ wepiki beleke ikaęž‰ hakokonaęž‰ yamemekeme.  
\v 7 Kutupa mo hande deto halaęž‰ tonkopu ale homekemaęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ enisolomanu paęž‰taęž‰ mo hoto paeyao pa hao halo paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ tumbiki watake hataęž‰ kawasomanu haleaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeaęž‰ lumumaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo tumbulu baeyaęž‰me. Kutupa mo tembolo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰pate pa mo watake hataęž‰ enisolo manumaęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ ke handaasaęž‰eki mea ipu paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ puaęž‰peke yaęž‰me.   
\c 16  
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki ulaęž‰ kawasomanu  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo tembolo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make wopumaęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ enisolo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kenkenaęž‰ pua mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki pambaęž‰laęž‰ watake hataęž‰ kawasomanu holaęž‰pe leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ titinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawaso kenkenaęž‰ pua holaeyaęž‰me. Kutu pieke handaa otaęž‰ hoke tanda tieke piki boleke manutaęž‰ mo hande hoke sayalenaęž‰ maka talaeme tapake make mo ale mandaęž‰ meao wepimiki ale paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeni pu haeme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitiaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Kutupa yaapo peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawaso mo dawala manda pua holaeyaęž‰me. Mo ikalitaęž‰ homeke halinaęž‰ wemaęž‰ handaataęž‰ koto dawala paęž‰taęž‰ pitimi ale paeyao homememe.   
\p
\v 4 Kutupa tepo peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawaso mea pua mo ikalimanu make opaęž‰laęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰manu holaeyaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ we au lolo yapeaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa mo ikalimanu handeteke hayaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ panisi pealuekemaęž‰ maĚ±leke liaasaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone waęž‰peleme. O otaęž‰ yako piki someo. Neke ame hale make ambaęž‰ hae makee.  
\v 6 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ we make mo potopede haliwekinaęž‰ we make holememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ame nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki make we ikali nenaęž‰ haleleme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yenki kone minaęž‰lememe laa leaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Kutupa mo oloda paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wele wopupiki Tekehali Kodaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ panisi pealuekemaęž‰ maĚ±leke liaasaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ tikitiki pea make otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ wepeleme leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo tonko peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawasotaęž‰ natenaęž‰ holaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa mo nate ipikaęž‰ wele wopu piki titipumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tenaęž‰ waleke haleaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ do wele wopupiki titipumaęž‰ to tokilieke handaataęž‰ mo ke manunaęž‰ handeteke hayaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki hoeyaememe. Kutu pimipate ikaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ hoki na walaa ipikaęž‰ wele tiekenaęž‰ biki na mea minaęž‰liaememe.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa mo yunki peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawasotaęž‰ mo hoke sayalenaęž‰ kini seanaęž‰ pua holaeyaęž‰me. Kutu pieke handaa timbaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo hande sayalenaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ tumbaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tanda tieke nalo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kekeke tankolo nememe.  
\v 11 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ tanda make tete manunaęž‰ oli hepeni halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki hoeyaemepate ikaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ hoki na walememe.   
\p
\v 12 Kutupa mo yunki mindiki peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawasotaęž‰ mo ikali tieke biki Yupoteitisinaęž‰ holaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa mo nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane haleme kini manunaęž‰ potaęž‰ wiaaso mo hande ikalitaęž‰ hapupa peaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kutupa kiĚ±maęž‰ handeke haĚ±iĚ± pambeke temoko tepo handoaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ mo popake itiki hake sinaęž‰ handeke alenaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hoke sayale hombelekenaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ make mo yayapiki potopedenaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ make pitaęž‰ opolu bao epememe.  
\v 14 Ikitaęž‰ mo na handeke haumanu pu haleme hoke temokomanue. Mo hoke temoko tepomaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ kinimanu pua hatuku mea aęž‰pa mo Wele Wopupiki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Aneke natenaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pinaęž‰ yeke pimikime.   
\p
\v 15 Opie. IĚ±taęž‰ pake nalaęž‰ hali leke ipulueke. UĚ± na peliki hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu wopu handeteke hao hale sometaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilieke. Ipikitaęž‰ paa tia pominolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali leke popelekenaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ meaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke pitaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 16 Kutupa mo hande temoko tepomaęž‰ mo kinimanu hatuku aęž‰pa mo Hibulu pimaęž‰taęž‰ Amakedoni laęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa mombaęž‰laeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 17 Kutupa mo watake peao enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kawasotaęž‰ oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ holaeyaęž‰me. Oni mo tembolo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aneke pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ koto paelaęž‰ handaęž‰e leaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kutupa ti tekelemanu make aęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ piki tutumanu make tutu tiekemanu make otaęž‰ hoke yu momeni make piaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ hali wepia kini pea aęž‰pa ame do make kutupiki yu momeni na paęž‰laęž‰pate do yu momeni homeketaęž‰ paeyao ankulake otaęž‰ hoke taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pikieki yaęž‰mee.  
\v 19 Mo aneke daonitaęž‰ tepo tekilipa mo kenke paeyaonaęž‰ daoni paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaeyaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Baęž‰biloni tieketaęž‰ pa niminaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wopu mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ waini ikali ipikaęž‰ kaponaęž‰ nenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Mo dawalamaęž‰ dupalaęž‰ kenkemanu paeyaotaęž‰ alu pao mo potemanu paeyaotaęž‰ alupaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Leke opeke ya hapeke tieke tiekemanu kaęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke hombeleke piki ekimanu oli ya nanemaęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰pa wandaęž‰hali manda lopeaęž‰me. Koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ke handaeyaęž‰ ya hapekenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki hoeyaememe. Pa ekipeke do ketaęž‰ otaęž‰ hokeeki yaęž‰mee.   
\c 17  
\s1 Hali yolo halaęž‰ biki wiki wandaęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa mo hande watake hataęž‰ kawaso miniki haeme watake hataęž‰ enisolo homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Epoe. IĚ±maęž‰ mo hali yolo halaęž‰ biki wiki wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ panisi walueke. Mo ikalimanu teaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰elaęž‰ aneke daoni hombelekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Do kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ kini manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± hoke loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau pu ombu haememe. Kutupa mo kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ waini ikali naa keaememe leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Mo Sipitidimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ e pokolo hataęž‰ mo enisolomaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ mea tia peaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo wepiki sayale maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hoki manda pitiaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. Mo sayalenaęž‰ loke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ kitaasaęž‰ bikimanu lao kutupa ipikitaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ amboke hao make kiki yaapo ekekemanu hayaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Mo wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰taęž‰ we taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaapo piki au lekeeki yameaęž‰me. Kutupa mo akaęž‰taęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki beleke manumaęž‰ make seliapo piki toopi manumaęž‰ make sekete inkiki manumaęž‰ make tumbulu baeyaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaalaęž‰piki ekimanu make haĚ±iĚ± pambeke alemanu make tumbulu baeyeke kolomaęž‰ wepiki kapo miniki hayaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo ipikaęž‰ wenokonaęž‰taęž‰ hande aęž‰mbaalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ biki dupa wiekeme. Hali yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make kikanaęž‰ haumanu pu haleme wandaęž‰hali make iki paeyaonaęž‰ inkiki Baęž‰biloni tieke laa wiaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaa pelia haemeke handa limiki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ we naĚ±aĚ± keayaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ moeki hando haotaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomuaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Mo enisolomaęž‰ IĚ± lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ ekipeke penkilipaęž‰tia pominelepe. IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰ mea tia pomu halaęž‰ sayalenaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teke la kionoe. Mo hande watake hataęž‰ amboke hao make kiki yaapo ekeke halaęž‰ sayalenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Koto sayaletaęž‰ ambaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hayaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ na daęž‰taa halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ ame do siki mo honiki na wiki naku kiake paęž‰taęž‰ hama opolu bao ipiki hoeyaenaęž‰ pelieke. Do kenkenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ do kenke aĚ±iĚ± na wepiki haenaęž‰ kone mo deto halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki na lake wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo hande sayale handolo hataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomilimikie. Ambaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hayaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ na deteke halaęž‰me. Pate paa opolo ipilieke.   
\p
\v 9 Doeki manutaęž‰ hone u lenkene pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapomaęž‰ handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ haue. Mo watake hataęž‰ amboketaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ yueli manue. Kototaęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ pilaęž‰ alenaęž‰e. Kutupa make ikitaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ kini manue.  
\v 10  Yunki hataęž‰taęž‰ lopelemepate homekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pa handeteke halaęž‰me. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipiki epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nate hosiki sikimaęž‰ homeke handeteke halieke.  
\v 11 Kutupa mo hande ambaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta hayaęž‰pate ame na daęž‰ta halaęž‰ sayaletaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone ketepo peao kinie. Mo hande watake hataęž‰ tapake konee. Ipikitaęž‰ hoeyaenaęž‰ pulaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Mo hande kiki yaapo ekeke manutaęž‰ kiki yaapo kini manue. Ikitaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na kini pea handeteke halemepate pa aowa homeke homekenaęž‰ mo hoke sayale ameĚ±leĚ± handeteke haenaęž‰ waleke halieke.  
\v 13 Do kiki yaapo ale ikitaęž‰ teke homeke homeke wia halememe. Ikaęž‰ honkopu make ikaęž‰ handeteke haleme wele manutaęž‰ mo sayale paęž‰taęž‰ halelememe.  
\v 14 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie. Pate mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wi laa yataęž‰paęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰ hone tulao haleme hoki nane tolu haleme tapake ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ mo tapake bepolalimikie. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ tekehali paeyaonaęž‰ Tekehali make kini paeyaonaęž‰ Kinie leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 15 Mo enisolomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Mo hande hande hali yolo halaęž‰ wandaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ ikali manutaęž‰ kapomani taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ kenkemanu make mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki wandaęž‰hali paeyao make mo tutu taęž‰taęž‰manu make pi taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ leke tapake manue.  
\v 16 Mo hande hande kiki yaapo ekeke manumaęž‰ make mo hande sayalemaęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ otaęž‰ honditi pilimikie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ pambalaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao holaęž‰ mea pa tia haenaęž‰ lelimikie. Mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ loke mindiki naa kutupa ti ulekemaęž‰ hoeyaalimikie.  
\v 17 Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki peaenaęž‰ yeke ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰manu ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki winaęž‰ leeke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea homeke tupaęž‰ hau pilimikie. Ikaęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ mo sayale paęž‰taęž‰ halaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu otaęž‰ peneme yaalo epenaęž‰ lelimikie.  
\v 18 Mo hande wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo aneke daoni hombelekee. Mo kenke honiki paeyaonaęž‰ kinimanu handeteke halaęž‰ daonie laa leaęž‰me.   
\c 18  
\s1 Baęž‰biloninaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Doeki hoki nanetaęž‰ enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ oli hepeni nane hao holaęž‰paęž‰nialo epeaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ wele tieke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu ipikaęž‰ yameeke leke yale yale piki paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do kenke paeyao paĚ±aĚ± peayaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tiekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi alo alotaęž‰  
\q1 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰me. Baęž‰biloni tieketaęž‰ lopaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Ipikitaęž‰ hoke temoko tonumaęž‰ make haĚ±iĚ± pambeke temokomanu haleme teke dae.  
\q1 Otaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± pambaęž‰papeke make handaęž‰ nalaęž‰ na piki anemone ba manutaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 3 Pa ekipeke mo kapomani taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ tapake paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ waini ikali nememe.  
\q1 Mo honkopu wopu hake waini ikali ipikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\q1 Do kenkenaęž‰ kini manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau pu ombu haememe.  
\q1 Kutupa do kenkenaęž‰ bisinisi haliwekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ kikanaęž‰ hau leke piaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ hamoko haememe leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ opuaęž‰pate oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Ya wandaęž‰halio. Opolu bao ipupee. Koto wandaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipupee.  
\q1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ na apaęž‰taapaęž‰pee. Ipikaęž‰ hoke yenki minaęž‰laęž‰eki na telipa miaęž‰paęž‰pee.   
\q1
\v 5 Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ oli hepeni wataalo aęž‰maęž‰elaęž‰me.  
\q1 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu hone niminaasaęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 6 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke tupaęž‰ pipee. Ipikaęž‰ piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ pa atulao halaęž‰pe.  
\q1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hokeeki nomenaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ amu peawayaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ kapo paęž‰taęž‰ mo yaapo peao honkopu wopu hake ikali tumbape.   
\q1
\v 7 Ipikaęž‰ kone mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki make taęž‰naęž‰ tieke paęž‰laęž‰eki make halolo piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone paa mo tanda tiekemanu make homenaęž‰ tupaęž‰ tanda minaęž‰laęž‰eki make halaęž‰pe.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Kini wandaęž‰ do pilu handaęž‰e. IĚ±taęž‰ kineke wandaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hamono tupaęž‰ tanda minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na handulueke laa alaęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 8 Do ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ke eleke elekemaęž‰ minilieke. Do ke manutaęž‰ yeni ki make homenaęž‰ tupaęž‰ tanda minaęž‰laęž‰eki make teaęž‰ ki makee. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ ti ulekemaęž‰ yankilieke.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke mo wandaęž‰ panisi peaasaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ wele wopu paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Do kenkenaęž‰ haleme kinimanu mo wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± loke apaęž‰tao hoke naęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu mandakenaęž‰ pimi tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ mo daoni tiekenaęž‰ eĚ± lelimikie. Mo yanko paeyaasaęž‰ ti ulekenaęž‰ lumu handolo hataęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Ikitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ tandataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ putupa meaęž‰peke yeke paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ papate leke halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰e. Otaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Do aneke make honkopu hake daoni Baęž‰bilonio. Nate leke homeke sikinaęž‰ kone neketaęž‰ panisi kaęž‰laęž‰me laa lelimikie.   
\p
\v 11 Do kenkenaęž‰ bisinisi haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ eĚ± alo make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ make homelememe. Pa ekipeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na hambelememe.  
\v 12 Ikaęž‰ kolo make silipa make seliapo piki toopimanu make sekete inkikimanu make dau pankaęž‰manu make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki wepiki daumanu make silika daumanu make mandane taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki wopu na halaęž‰ timanu make elepaęž‰ntinaęž‰ ekekemaęž‰ waęž‰pele taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki alemanu make yenki tieke wiki timanu make kopamaęž‰ handeke ale botonosi make ayenimaęž‰ wepiki alemanu make kalasimaęž‰ handeke hakesapo biki mambolo  
\v 13 make mandane ti manunaęž‰ yonkeleke make teikaęž‰maęž‰ handeke ale make totopo yole piki ale make hosiki timaęž‰ handeke maetamo leke ti make totopo wopu piki oeta make waini ikali make pa oeta make palaowa make widi make kao make sipisipi make hosi make hosi maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ yolaa pulaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰ka mendeke make e pa hameke pokaaseme haliweki make halinaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ame do hambaęž‰peke na yaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Mo bisinisi haliwekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ ekie laa Nakaęž‰ hande wia hae epeke ale manutaęž‰ alu paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa nakaęž‰ hande hamoko hale alemanu make neke au le yole paęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ alu paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ paa na handaęž‰ wilipikie laa lelimikie.   
\p
\v 15 Koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ bisinisi pitolo hataęž‰ hamoko haeme bisinisi haliwekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ papate pua halimikie. Pa ekipeke mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ tanda putupa mea pekeyeke loaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± alo make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolotaęž‰ do lelimikie.  
\v 16 Mo aneke daoni hombeleketaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰e otaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ hakepiki akaęž‰ pankaęž‰maęž‰ make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki wepiki daumaęž‰ make yama kutupa kolomaęž‰ wepiki beleke manumaęž‰ make seliapo piki toopi manumaęž‰ make sekete inkikimaęž‰ make dupao yamaęž‰tiki pu hayaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Pate nateleke homeke sikinaęž‰ kone do hamoko alemanu paeyao alu paeyaęž‰me.  
\p Mo dawalanaęž‰ sipi you haliweki make mo sipinaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pimi wandaęž‰hali make mo sipinaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki make mo dawalanaęž‰ ane mone e pokeme wandaęž‰hali paeyao make papate haememe.  
\v 18 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ mea neliayaęž‰ ti ulekenaęž‰ lumu handolo hataęž‰ eĚ± wi tieke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dupiki aneke daoni hombeleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hayaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Ikaęž‰ ambokeninaęž‰ dokolo mea lopaaso hataęž‰ eĚ± alo make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰e. Otaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Mo koto aneke daoni otaęž‰ paalaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hamoko halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo dawalanaęž‰ pominaęž‰laęž‰ sipi teke haliwekitaęž‰ hamoko haememe. Kutupa nateleke homekenaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao alu paeyaęž‰me lememe.   
\p
\v 20 Hepenio taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ hoeyaalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make mo aposolo haliweki make potopede haliweki make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰pee. Pa ekipeke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki hoeyaalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 21 Kutupa wele wopu piki enisolomaęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke piki toopi tieke mea oni dawala paęž‰taęž‰ yombu lopaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hande aneke daoni Baęž‰bilonitaęž‰ dupa anekemaęž‰ mea lopaęž‰niao otaęž‰ pa na handolo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰e.  
\v 22 Mo kidamaęž‰ handeke alenaęž‰ eĚ± make wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemanu make mo soke lu haleme wandaęž‰hali make mo bu kanake make neke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na opilimikie. Kutupa mo ane mone e pokeleme haliwekitaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na halimikie. Kutupa mo palaowa yombitaęž‰laęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki toopinaęž‰ eĚ± make otaęž‰ na opilimikie.  
\v 23 Lamepanaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na handilimikie. Kutupa mo halinaęž‰ da panake pulaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ make wandaęž‰ panake minaęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make make otaęž‰ na opilimikie. Nakaęž‰ bisinisi haliwekitaęž‰ kenke honiki paeyao lu tumbao honkopu wopu haeme make nakaęž‰ yayapiki haĚ±iĚ±piki tiĚ±oĚ± haumanu pi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao makeaememe laa leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 24 Baęž‰biloni panisi peake hautaęž‰ mo potopede haliweki make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ wetaęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ wieke piaęž‰me. Otaęž‰e. Mo kenkenaęž‰ liaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ we paeyao wiaęž‰me.   
\c 19  
\p
\v 1 Doeki hoki nanetaęž‰ oli hepeni nane wandaęž‰hali tiekemaęž‰ leke nono pea alotaęž‰ Haleluya. (Nikaęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki miniliamanaęž‰e) Daęž‰taęž‰mono yeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki make paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki make wele tieke make nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ipikaęž‰ pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰eki make tikitiki pikieki makee. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hali yolo hayaęž‰ wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumaęž‰ kenke paeyao hoeyaeyeke handaa ketete peleme laa maĚ±leke liaataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ panisi pealaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaeyaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali lu homaeyeke handaa loaęž‰me laa lememe.   
\p
\v 3 Paa eĚ± wi alo alotaęž‰ Haleluya. Mo hande aneke daoni mea neliayaęž‰ lumutaęž‰ honiki na wiki hoto paeyao pa aęž‰meiyu halaęž‰me lememe.  
\v 4 Mo hali tieke homekenaęž‰ tonkopu you haliweki make mo deto haleme tonkopu ale manumaęž‰ make pandaęž‰puniao lopa mo kini seanaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pimime. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutu pinaęž‰e. Haleluya lememe.  
\v 5 Kutupa mo kini sea paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaaseme tapake make ipiki yeiyaęž‰ laaseme wandaęž‰hali make iki paeyaomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki miniliapee. Mo aneke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make natehali wandaęž‰halisunu paęž‰taęž‰ make loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\s1 Mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ ne pambaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 6 Kutupa eĚ± alaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali hombutaęž‰ hombeleke hataęž‰ make ikali dou lopolo make tutu tieke litolo make leke nono piaęž‰eki dupa opuaęž‰me. Haleluya. Mo Tekehali nikaęž‰ Aneke Kodaęž‰taęž‰ kini halaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ niki paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homomanaęž‰e. Ipikaęž‰ tieke halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ biki mea miniliamanaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke mo hande Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ opolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ panake wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo ekinaęž‰ ambaęž‰ tikitiki yao halaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ hake pea leke yale yale piki dau yamenaęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰me laa lememe. Koto dautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ epeke hau piteleme ekie.   
\p
\v 9 Kutupa mo enisolomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Doeki laaniae. Mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ne pambaęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ epoaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰pee. Kutupa mo enisolomaęž‰ apaęž‰taaso alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanue leaęž‰me.  
\v 10 IĚ±taęž‰ ipiki yeiyaęž‰ lao yeni puluku alo ipikaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao lopoaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ei IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kotoeki na piaęž‰pema. IĚ±taęž‰ e pokaaso nakaęž‰ yankekee. Kutupa make nakaęž‰ kamemanu mo Yesumaęž‰ peneme yaeyaęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu miniki haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yankeke halome. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pu hapeke laa leaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Yesumaęž‰ peneme yaeyaęž‰ otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo potopede haliwekimaęž‰ alemeeki hone u tiaasaęž‰ekie.   
\s1 Mo hakepiki hosi maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pilaęž‰ hali  
\p
\v 11 Kutupa oli hepeni lumbaęž‰pa wia mo hakepiki hosi maęž‰naęž‰ handoaęž‰me. Mo hosi hokinaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kimaęž‰ na homeke hone tu laalaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ Otaęž‰eki yaapoe leaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tikitiki piki haumaęž‰ pi yokaalu pea make ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipulaęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu halaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Ipikaęž‰ leketaęž‰ titipu pupapeke ti haleke ekimaęž‰ handaa ipikaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰taęž‰ kini you akaęž‰ eleke eleke pambaeyaęž‰me. Biki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo somenaęž‰ laeyaęž‰pate koto bikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hone na ulaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ homeke hone ulaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Ipikaęž‰ pambaeyeke akaęž‰ hokulutaęž‰ wemaęž‰ tote piaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pie.  
\v 14 Mo hepeninaęž‰ ami manumaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki teliaęž‰ mea pememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hakepiki hosi manda pitaęž‰ hakepiki akaęž‰ yamememe.  
\v 15 Ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ kapomani paeyaomaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ tapake lu bepolaenaęž‰ ne wopu hake bainasi opolu baeyaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ayeni dopitamaęž‰ iki handeteke hataęž‰ mo Aneke Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰ piki mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ waini dekepo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa ulaęž‰ waini daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ tumba bepilieke.  
\v 16 Ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰ hokulunaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ palekenaęž‰ maketaęž‰ biki dupa laeyaęž‰me. Kini paeyaonaęž‰ kinie laa Tekehali paeyaonaęž‰ Tekehalie.   
\p
\v 17 Kutupa mo natenaęž‰ tiao hayaęž‰ enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ handoaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ya tukikinaęž‰ aĚ±eĚ±yaĚ± pomimi bamanu paęž‰taęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wi laęž‰moneaaso alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aneke yawe litaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombaęž‰laęž‰pee laataęž‰  
\v 18 Aęž‰pa mo kini manunaęž‰ make ami you haliwekinaęž‰ make ami titinaęž‰ loke make paeyao aęž‰pa napee. Kutupa hosi maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ loke make hosi mea pomu haleme haliwekinaęž‰ loke make wandaęž‰hali paeyao pa hameke e pokaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke make pa haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke make natehali wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke make aneke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke paeyao aęž‰pa napee leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 Kutupa mo hande sayale tieke hombeleke make do kenkenaęž‰ kinimanu make ikaęž‰ ami paeyaomaęž‰ mo hande hosi hokinaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ hali pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ami ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ mombelememe.  
\v 20 Mo sayale make mo sayalenaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ na handeke haumanu piaęž‰ makeaaso potopede hali make dipula minimime. Koto piaęž‰ na handeke hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo sayalenaęž‰ tombo ikaęž‰ wenokonaęž‰ wimi wandaęž‰hali make mo mandaęž‰ meao wepimi sayale paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pimi wandaęž‰hali make makeaeyaęž‰me. Mo sayale tieke hombeleke pitaęž‰ mo makeaaso potopede hali yaapo pa pitiki oni titipupiki lankaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ solopa talaęž‰ ti uleke kiake paęž‰taęž‰ lopaememe.  
\v 21 Ikaęž‰ ami tititaęž‰ mo hosi maęž‰naęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ halinaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeaęž‰ bainasimaęž‰ lu petepete piaęž‰me. Kutupa mo ba manumaęž‰ mo tokomanu naakaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ weleke anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalimikie.   
\c 20  
\s1 Bapimanu 1 daoseni  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰ oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ hao holopolo ipulu ipikaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo honiki na wiki naku tieke kiakenaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ ki make kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke piki seni miniki epeaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande popake itiki hake sitaęž‰ hande ambisanake hao hayaęž‰ keto kototaęž‰ hande Depolo o Sadani laęž‰laęž‰ aletaęž‰ mina 1 daoseni bapi manunaęž‰ senimaęž‰ tonkaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Mo enisolomaęž‰taęž‰ mo sitaęž‰ oni naku tieke kiake paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea lokaęž‰ hao aęž‰mbo pambeaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo simaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke paeyao haleme tapake taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ makeaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo 1 daoseni bapimanu paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ opolu baenaęž‰yeke piaęž‰me. Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ nateleke hosiki siki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalieke.   
\p
\v 4 Kutupa kini seamanu handoaęž‰me. Koto seanaęž‰ pitimi haliwekitaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu pimi wele haleaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo hande Yesumaęž‰ peneme yaeyaęž‰ otaęž‰eki waleme ekinaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi waleme ekinaęž‰ limiki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ temokomanu handoaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande sayale tieke hombeleke make ipiki mandaęž‰ meao wepimiki ale yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni na pimi make ikaęž‰ wenoko o popeke nane kikinaęž‰ mo sayalenaęž‰ maka na mimikime. Ikitaęž‰ paa daęž‰ta hataęž‰ 1 daoseni bapi manunaęž‰ Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± kini pitaęž‰ handeteke haememe.  
\v 5 Do ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki mea tiaasaęž‰ekie. Mo mandane wopu homemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na daęž‰ta tiao haemepate mo 1 daoseni bapimanu hoki nane detenaęž‰ piaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Mo mandane homeme wandaęž‰halimanu do titinaęž‰ mea tiaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰taemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ laa yako pinaęž‰ lelieke. Mo yaapo peao homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki wataapeketaęž‰ honkopu na ulaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Ketiso yaaponaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ haliweki hataęž‰ 1 daoseni bapimanu ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± handeteke halimikie.   
\s1 Sadani bepolaasaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 7 Mo 1 daoseni bapimanu paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Sadanitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dipula pilaęž‰eki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalieke.  
\v 8 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke honiki honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ tapake paeyao makealieke. Kototaęž‰ Koko pitaęž‰ Meikoko leke tapakee. Sadanimaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hatuku ipilieke. Mo tapaketaęž‰ mo dawala hou manumaęž‰ handilimikie.  
\v 9 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kenke tieke tumbaaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mombeleme alenaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ daoni make pua popei yaememe. Pate ti uleke oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa lopaa paeyao hoeyaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰hali makeaeyaęž‰ Sadanitaęž‰ oni ti uleke kiake make titipupiki lankaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki solopa paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea lopaeyaęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande sayale tieke hombeleke make mo makeaaso potopede hali make lopalaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰e. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki make natepa yolao hoto paeyao puki tandamaęž‰ homo halimikie.   
\s1 Paeyaaso pi yokaalu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 11 Kutupa mo hakepiki kini sea tieke pitaęž‰ mo seanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ hali yaapo handoaęž‰me. Kutupa mo kenke ya yaapotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ na haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ pa pindipa pualu pitolo hataęž‰ alupaepeme.  
\v 12 Kutupa mo homemeke wandaęž‰hali aneke make natehali make paeyao mandakenaęž‰ mo kini seanaęž‰ puki tikitiki haemeeki handoaęž‰me. Buka manutaęž‰ lumbiaęž‰me. Kutupa buka maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ buka lumbiaęž‰me. Mo homemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ mo buka manunaęž‰ lao wieke tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimiki tupaęž‰ siki kone maĚ±leke lia telipiaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kutupa mo dawalamaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali haleaęž‰me. Kutupa homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make mo homo halaęž‰ kenkemaęž‰ make ipilikaęž‰ wia haepe toko halepeme. Kutupa paeyaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimiki tupaęž‰ siki kone anaęž‰naęž‰ maĚ±leke lia telipiaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa homaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ homo halaęž‰ kenke yaapotaęž‰ oni ti uleke paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea lopaeyaęž‰me. Do ti uleke kiaketaęž‰ yaapo peao homaęž‰laęž‰ekie.  
\v 15 Kutupa make maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ na laeyaęž‰ sometaęž‰ oni ti uleke kiake paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea lopaeyaęž‰me.   
\c 21  
\s1 Panake hepeni pitaęž‰ panake kenke yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ panake hepeni pitaęž‰ panake kenke yaapo handoaęž‰me. Titinaęž‰ hepeni pitaęž‰ kenke yaapotaęž‰ alupaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa mo dawala make loaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Mo hande Yakopiki Daoni hande panake Diutuselemetaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki maĚ±landi puluekemaęž‰ amu pea tikitiki yao ipulu pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰eki handoaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Oli kini sea nanemaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tiekemaęž‰ dupa leaęž‰eki opuaęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ dataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali au lalieke. Kodaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± halieke. Ipikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halieke.  
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ eĚ± pankekemanu honialieke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki pa na handilimikie. Kutupa puki tanda pitolo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make eĚ± alaęž‰eki make tanda minaęž‰laęž‰eki make otaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰lieke. Mo ambaęž‰ haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ alu paeyaęž‰me laa leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 5 Kutupa mo kini seanaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao panakeeki wepitolome leaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alotaęž‰ Do ekitaęž‰ laaniae. Pa ekipeke do pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰eki yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make otaęž‰ hone tu lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ pie leaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa ombu alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ pu paelaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ titinaęž‰ make sale nane makee. Kini pitolo make paeyaaso makee. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo opaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ ikalitaęž‰ na hambeke pa nenaęž‰ waleke halueke.  
\v 7 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ peaa bepolaasaęž‰ hali hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ doeki minaęž‰e. IĚ±taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halueke. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ yaka weki au lalueke.  
\v 8 Pate hone pamboneke tapake make baęž‰saęž‰ piteleme tapake make ataęž‰kaęž‰ peaaseme tapake make honemaęž‰ kone hali lu homaaseme tapake make pake nalo loke apaęž‰taaseme tapake make tiĚ±oĚ± hau pu haleme tapake make toopi ti wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu haleme tapake make mo yayapiki pi lo haleme tapake make paeyaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ oni ti uleke kiake make titipupiki lankaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki solopa bu lo halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰e. Koto hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo yaapo peao homaęž‰laęž‰ekie.   
\s1 Panake Diutuseleme  
\p
\v 9 Mo hande paeyaaso watake hataęž‰ ke handaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ tumbulu baake kawaso miniki haeme hande watake hataęž‰ enisolo homekemaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ walono epoe leaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Mo Sipitidimaęž‰ IĚ± tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokolo hataęž‰ mo enisolomaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ oli pote tieke tumikinaęž‰ mea tia peaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo panake Diutuseleme hande yakopiki daoni oli hepeni nane Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ hao holopolo epeaęž‰eki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Mo daonitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± piti paĚ±aĚ± putia ipulu hataęž‰ diaęž‰sepa leke toopi seliapomaęž‰ handa alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leke kalasimaęž‰ handeekeme.  
\v 12 Mo daonitaęž‰ hokulupiki pape tiekemaęž‰ popei yao potaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ paeyao kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo lombayaęž‰me. Mo potaęž‰ kake yalaotaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo enisolomaęž‰ handeteke haememe. Mo potaęž‰ kake manunaęž‰ yalaotaęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo tapakenaęž‰ biki laeyaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Mo nepokomanu yalaotaęž‰ potaęž‰kake tepo lo lombayaęž‰me. Nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanetaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake tepo lombayaęž‰me. Nepoko yaapo nane make potaęž‰ kake tepo tepo lo lombayaęž‰me. Oni nate pambaęž‰laęž‰ nane make potaęž‰ kake tepo lombayaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Mo daoninaęž‰ papetaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo pinki nonopiki toopi oto tiekenaęž‰ noko peekeme. Koto toopi manunaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikikinaęž‰ aposolo hali kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ biki laeyaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 15 Mo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi la kiaęž‰ enisolotaęž‰ mo daoni make ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ kakemanu make ipikaęž‰ pape paęž‰laęž‰eki make paeyao tombo muluekemaęž‰ mo kolomaęž‰ wepiki tombo minaęž‰laęž‰ tolo miniki hayaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Mo daoninaęž‰ petipeke maka make mo hokulu maka make otaęž‰ homeke make paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo enisolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tombo minaęž‰laęž‰ dolomaęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ tombo miaęž‰me. Mo daonitaęž‰ 2 daoseninaęž‰ 400 kilomida otaęž‰ hokulu pea make petipeke yaęž‰laęž‰eki make olinaęž‰ hokulu paęž‰laęž‰eki make homeke hau kone piekeme.  
\v 17 Kutupa mo enisolomaęž‰ ombu mo daoninaęž‰ pape polopalaęž‰eki tombo miaęž‰pate otaęž‰ 60 mida miaęž‰me. Mo tombo minaęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ hokulu piki ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone tombo miaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 18 Mo papetaęž‰ diaęž‰sepa leke toopimaęž‰ wepiekeme. Kutupa mo daonitaęž‰ kolomaęž‰ handa alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leke kalasimaęž‰ handeaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Mo daoninaęž‰ papenaęž‰ pinki toopi manunaęž‰taęž‰ ane mone seliapopiki toopi manumaęž‰ popei yao otaęž‰ lu liaeyekeme. Titinaęž‰ toopi pinkitaęž‰ biki diaęž‰sepa yekeme. Yaapo peao toopi pinkinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ saęž‰paeya yekeme. Tepo peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ aęž‰keidi yekeme. Tonko peao ekitaęž‰ ambumaęž‰ handeke au leke toopi biki emulolidi yekeme.  
\v 20 Yunki peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ onkisi yekeme. Yunki mindiki hataęž‰ peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ kaniliani yekeme. Watake hataęž‰ peao ekitaęž‰ hamipiki toopi biki kotisalaedi yekeme. Ketepo peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ betili yekeme. NoĚ±iĚ± peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ topaęž‰si yekeme. Kiki yaapo peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ kotisapoteisi yekeme. Kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ homeke peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ dieisini yekeme. Kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo peao ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ aęž‰metisi yekeme.  
\v 21 Mo kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo potaęž‰ kake manutaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo sekete hapekemanu yekeme. Mo potaęž‰ kake manunaęž‰ yalaotaęž‰ mo sekete hapekemaęž‰ wepumaęž‰ wepumaęž‰ piekeme. Mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taleke kalasimaęž‰ handeke kolomaęž‰ pilaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 22 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ tembolo da na handoaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Aneke Tekehali Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo hande Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki yaapotaęž‰ mo tembolo da yekeme.  
\v 23 Mo daoninaęž‰taęž‰ nate o kaisepo maęž‰ndaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pealuekemaęž‰ opaęž‰peke na yaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ au laęž‰laęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pu halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo daoninaęž‰ olaęž‰paketaęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki yaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Koto kenke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ pomilimikie. Kutupa mo kenkenaęž‰ kini manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hamoko ale manutaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea ipilimikie.  
\v 25 Mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake manutaęž‰ nate paeyao pa lombaęž‰pa wilieke. Otaęž‰ na pokilieke. Pa ekipeke koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki otaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰lieke.  
\v 26 Mo kenkenaęž‰ aneke make hamoko ale paeyaotaęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ mea ipilimikie.  
\v 27 Pate mo haĚ±iĚ± piki alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ na hondaęž‰ pambilieke. Koto tupaęž‰ kone maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ yaalaęž‰piki haumanu pu o yayapiki pi lo halaęž‰ some make na hondaęž‰ pambilieke. Mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ biki laalaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali homeke koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambilimikie.   
\c 22  
\s1 Daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kitaęž‰laęž‰ ikali pitaęž‰ ti yaapo  
\p
\v 1 Mo enisolomaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leke kalasimaęž‰ handeke daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kitaęž‰laęž‰ ikali yopulu halaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰me. Mo ikalitaęž‰ oli Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki yaaponaęž‰ kini sea paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutupa mo ikalitaęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰ tukikinaęž‰ yapeaęž‰me. Mo ikali teaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰taęž‰ hande daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kitaęž‰laęž‰ ti opo halaęž‰me. Mo timaęž‰taęž‰ bapi homekenaęž‰taęž‰ sumbaęž‰ homeke homeke yalao kiliki aęž‰eyaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ katake manutaęž‰ mo tapake taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ekie.  
\v 3 Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoeyaenaęž‰ laa maĚ±leke lia ulaęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na wilieke.  
\p Mo Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo Sipisipi Maęž‰naęž‰ Ikiki yaaponaęž‰ kini seataęž‰ koto daoni paęž‰taęž‰ wilieke. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pu halimikie.  
\v 4 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke handaa make ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wenokoninaęž‰ laalimikie.  
\v 5 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki otaęž‰ diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ olaęž‰pake make natenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± make na weilimikie. Pa ekipeke mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± halieke. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kinimanu pitaęž‰ hoto paeyao handeteke hao halimikie.   
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 6 Kutupa mo enisolomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰eki yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone tu lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa hande potopede haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Sipitidi halo paęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ame do koto kone pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu walenaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ enisolo tapaalaęž‰me leaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opie. IĚ±taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulume. Do buka paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ opua pu haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie.   
\p
\v 8 IĚ± Dionimaęž‰ do hau paeyao handaa make opuaęž‰me. Kutupa do haumanu handa make opu paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do haumanu waleaęž‰ enisolonaęž‰ anketeke paęž‰taęž‰ lopa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ laaluekemaęž‰ pituaęž‰pate  
\v 9 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotoeki na piaęž‰pema laataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ e pokaaso nakaęž‰ yankekee. Kutupa make mo hande nakaęž‰ potopede kame manunaęž‰ make do bukanaęž‰ ulaęž‰ wapenaęž‰ opua pitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ yankeke kone halome. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke yeiyaęž‰ laaso hataęž‰ yeni pu hapeke laa leaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Kutupa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Do bukanaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ na aęž‰mbao wiaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke do haumanu paeyaonaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoke temoko haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke hau homeke pa pu hapeke. Epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ±piki some pu haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ±piki hau homeke pa pu hapeke. Epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ epeke some haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau homeke pa pu hapeke. Kutupa epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ yakopiki some haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ yako piki hau homeke pa pu hapeke.   
\p
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opie. IĚ±taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ homeke homeke peleme tupaęž‰ kone anaęž‰naęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo halo polo alemanu mea ipulume.  
\v 13 IĚ±taęž‰ titinaęž‰ make sale nane makee. Kini pitolo make paeyaaso makee laa leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 Epi amedamaęž‰ ikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu tandaęž‰pa hake peaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰ tinaęž‰ kiliki nenaęž‰ make mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ penaęž‰ make waleke halieke.  
\v 15 Pate mo ataęž‰kaęž‰ peaaseme tapake make tiĚ±oĚ± hau pu haleme tapake make pake nalo loke apaęž‰taaseme tapake make honemaęž‰ kone hali lu homaaseme tapake make toopi ti wepiaęž‰ ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau pu haleme tapake make yayapiki ekinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa pu haleme tapake make paeyao sikitaęž‰ mo daoni teaęž‰naęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane halememe.  
\v 16 IĚ±taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ do hau manutaęž‰ iki siosimanu haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ lawaenaęž‰ yaka enisolo tapaalome. Deipiditaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰mei halie. IĚ±taęž‰ mo hande da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso opaęž‰laęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke piki hombulankaęž‰e laa leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 17 Mo Sipitidi pitaęž‰ mo hali panake pulaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epoe alaęž‰me. Do pi opilimi tapake paeyaomaęž‰ make Epoe lapaęž‰peke yaęž‰lieke. Ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homele some epitaęž‰ do daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ ikalitaęž‰ pa hameke kitaęž‰laęž‰ekie laa meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Dotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi hone paęž‰laęž‰ somenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 18 IĚ±taęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ do laęž‰ ulaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ pimanu opiteleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi dupa alome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ apaęž‰taeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto some ipikaęž‰ panisi paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do bukanaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ kemanu handaęž‰pekeeki apaęž‰taalieke.  
\v 19 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do bukanaęž‰ ulaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ pimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea baeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto some ipikaęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ tinaęž‰ kiliki mulupaęž‰laęž‰ yenkinaęž‰ putupilikitaęž‰ pao mea make mo hande yakopiki daoni pua hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰eki make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pao milieke. Do bukanaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 20 Do wape paęž‰laęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ pie laa laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulume leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kutu piaęž‰peke. Tekehali Yesuo. Epoe.   
\p
\v 21 Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e.   